    # "I hope it’s a nurse other than Anna. I pray that it’s anyone else."
    "我希望那位护士不是安娜 。我祈祷是别的人。"

# game/script.rpy:659
translate chinese start_a66abd11:

    # "The door opens. The doctor comes in, and a step behind him is a nurse that is {i}not{/i} Anna."
    "门开了。医生走了进来，而跟在他后面的护士{i}不是{/i} 安娜。"

# game/script.rpy:660
translate chinese start_68ec1191:

    # "I sigh in relief."
    "我长吁一口气。"

# game/script.rpy:672
translate chinese start_64740d76:

    # doc "In a lot of pain, huh?"
    doc "很疼是吧？"

# game/script.rpy:674
translate chinese start_a520cfcd:

    # j "No, no, it's not that, doctor."
    j "不不，不是那样的，医生。"

# game/script.rpy:675
translate chinese start_eb395499:

    # j "But, well—"
    j "但是，额——"

# game/script.rpy:677
translate chinese start_d5a9596f:

    # doc "It can wait."
    doc "别急。"

# game/script.rpy:678
translate chinese start_bd7f27e2:

    # doc "Unless it’s urgent?"
    doc "难道有什么紧急的事？"

# game/script.rpy:680
translate chinese start_122901cf:

    # j "It’s... not."
    j "没什么……"

# game/script.rpy:682
translate chinese start_888dc77a:

    # doc "Very well then."
    doc "那好吧。"

# game/script.rpy:686
translate chinese start_29cf02c9:

    # "The doctor can't be over thirty-five years old."
    "那医生看起来不过35岁。"

# game/script.rpy:687
translate chinese start_38fd11fb:

    # "He's wearing a golden watch and fine-looking leather shoes."
    "他戴着金手表穿着好皮鞋。"

# game/script.rpy:688
translate chinese start_afb49fe4:

    # "He doesn’t look like a doctor to me at all. More like a businessman."
    "他看起来更像是一位生意人而不是一位医生。"

# game/script.rpy:689
translate chinese start_53528a68:

    # "The doctor goes from bed to bed with the nurse, checking on the patients, spending no more than a minute with each."
    "医生和护士一张床接着一张床地检查病人，每个病人都不超过一分钟。"

# game/script.rpy:690
translate chinese start_205f3730:

    # "He comes to my bed last."
    "他最后走到我的床前。"

# game/script.rpy:697
translate chinese start_f624df66:

    # doc "Okay, Mr. Friday..."
    doc "好的，辛奇伍先生……"

# game/script.rpy:698
translate chinese start_202cadaf:

    # doc "What was it, again? Let’s see here."
    doc "你刚刚说什么来着？让我看看。"

# game/script.rpy:702
translate chinese start_9089c8b2:

    # "He leafs through some papers and clicks his tongue."
    "他随手翻阅了一下我的病历，然后咂了咂舌头。"

# game/script.rpy:704
translate chinese start_66bc1f50:

    # doc "Ah. You fell."
    doc "啊。你摔倒了。"

# game/script.rpy:706
translate chinese start_984f6b91_1:

    # j "...Yeah."
    j "……是的。"

# game/script.rpy:708
translate chinese start_6765396d:

    # doc "How the hell did you manage to do that?"
    doc "你到底是怎么做到的？"

# game/script.rpy:709
translate chinese start_f5c1ab5f:

    # doc "Oh."
    doc "哦。"

# game/script.rpy:710
translate chinese start_620ec59d:

    # doc "These ’substances’ we found in your blood work explain {i}that{/i} mystery."
    doc "我们在你血液里发现的这些“物质”解释了{i}这个{/i} 谜团。"

# game/script.rpy:711
translate chinese start_0c6f5a9d:

    # doc "Not very clever, are you?"
    doc "看来你不是很聪明啊，是吧？"

# game/script.rpy:712
translate chinese start_084e450c:

    # doc "Getting high and—"
    doc "嗑药磕大了然后——"

# game/script.rpy:714
translate chinese start_0e6f69d7:

    # nurse "Doctor! You can’t say that."
    nurse "医生！你不能说那个。"

# game/script.rpy:716
translate chinese start_a0071780:

    # doc "Oh, sue me."
    doc "哦，有本事你起诉我啊。"

# game/script.rpy:717
translate chinese start_3dec0a99:

    # doc "And you, don’t do it again. Next time I won’t patch you up, you hear?"
    doc "还有你，别再那样做了。下一次我可就不给你收拾烂摊子了，听清了吗？"

# game/script.rpy:719
translate chinese start_3ede0869:

    # j "I’ll try not to."
    j "我尽力。"

# game/script.rpy:721
translate chinese start_1247b3fb:

    # "He’s being rude, but it doesn’t really bother me. I've got more important things on my mind."
    "他很粗鲁，但这不影响。我有更重要的事情在心头。"

# game/script.rpy:723
translate chinese start_6544cbb5:

    # j "Doctor, how long until I can start walking? At least with crutches?"
    j "医生，我什么时候才能下地走路？拄拐的那种也行。"

# game/script.rpy:735
translate chinese start_59b5fe2e:

    # doc "I don't know."
    doc "我不清楚。"

# game/script.rpy:737
translate chinese start_a475dd4c:

    # j "What?"
    j "什么？"

# game/script.rpy:739
translate chinese start_8faeff8a:

    # doc "What?"
    doc "怎么了？"

# game/script.rpy:741
translate chinese start_82ca5bf4:

    # j "You... you’re a doctor, aren’t you? My doctor?"
    j "你……你是个医生，对吧？是我的主治医生吧？"

# game/script.rpy:743
translate chinese start_a9146de1:

    # doc "The very same."
    doc "是啊。"

# game/script.rpy:744
translate chinese start_86e8b38f:

    # doc "Who do you think operated on you?"
    doc "不然是谁给你动的手术？"

# game/script.rpy:746
translate chinese start_034314d4:

    # "I look down at my leg. I'm suddenly very unsure of what I’ll see when the cast comes off."
    "我低头看着自己的腿，突然很不确定石膏取下来后里面会是什么样子。"

# game/script.rpy:748
translate chinese start_d08b33e8:

    # j "Can’t you at least {i}guess{/i} when I’ll be able to walk?"
    j "那你能不能至少{i}估计一下{/i}我什么时候能下地走路？"

# game/script.rpy:750
translate chinese start_4b9c62f9:

    # doc "I’d rather not."
    doc "还是算了吧。"

# game/script.rpy:752
translate chinese start_376f7f73:

    # "The nurse, standing next to the doctor, looks uncomfortable. She's holding a hand to her forehead and sighing."
    "站在医生旁边的护士看起来很不舒服，她用一只手捂着额头，叹了口气。"

# game/script.rpy:754
translate chinese start_93f07ad6:

    # j "But why not? Don’t I deserve to know?"
    j "但是为什么不可以？我难道没有知晓的权利吗？"

# game/script.rpy:756
translate chinese start_33342888:

    # doc "Well, a lot of factors are at play here, you see."
    doc "好吧，这涉及到复杂的因素，你懂的。"

# game/script.rpy:758
translate chinese start_4a74977e:

    # "The doctor starts moving his right hand in complex patterns."
    "医生开始用他的右手比比划划。"

# game/script.rpy:760
translate chinese start_80f77b46:

    # doc "Plenty of factors can change how quickly you heal. A whole lot. So who can really say?"
    doc "很多因素都会影响你痊愈的速度，非常多。所以有谁能说得准呢？"

# game/script.rpy:762
translate chinese start_823dc3c6:

    # j "Factors like what?"
    j "很多因素，例如什么？"

# game/script.rpy:764
translate chinese start_21c8dc42:

    # doc "Oh, so many of them."
    doc "哦，它们实在是太多了。"

# game/script.rpy:766
translate chinese start_6f5ed7f5:

    # j "Like {i}what?{/i}"
    j "例如{i}什么{/i}？"

# game/script.rpy:768
translate chinese start_72cd0df0:

    # doc "Like, uh..."
    doc "例如，额……"

# game/script.rpy:770
translate chinese start_9909a2c2:

    # "He glances down at his papers."
    "他低头看了一眼我的病历"

# game/script.rpy:772
translate chinese start_c86be506:

    # doc "...Like your blood pressure. Which is crap, by the way."
    doc "……例如你的血压。顺便说一下，它简直是一团乱麻。"

# game/script.rpy:773
translate chinese start_bb8449a6:

    # doc "Are you stressing over something?"
    doc "你在为什么事紧张吗？"

# game/script.rpy:775
translate chinese start_ce147a6b:

    # "Yes."
    "是的。"

# game/script.rpy:777
translate chinese start_1dd4185e:

    # j "No."
    j "没有。"

# game/script.rpy:778
translate chinese start_225041a3:

    # j "No, doctor. I'm not. I’m fine."
    j "不，医生。我没有。我很好。"

# game/script.rpy:780
translate chinese start_ab17c22f:

    # "He frowns a little."
    "他皱了一下眉头。"

# game/script.rpy:782
translate chinese start_f415e6ea:

    # doc "Well, you’ll be fine. Kick your feet back and relax."
    doc "好吧，你会没事的。少闹腾点放轻松就是了。"

# game/script.rpy:783
translate chinese start_e8b95c74:

    # doc "What’re you in such a hurry for, anyway? You haven’t got a job waiting for you outside or anything."
    doc "你这么着急干什么？你又没有紧急的工作或是别的事要处理。"

# game/script.rpy:785
translate chinese start_9fbca821:

    # j "Huh?"
    j "啥？"

# game/script.rpy:786
translate chinese start_df9c0fcf:

    # j "How do you know that?"
    j "你怎么知道的？"

# game/script.rpy:788
translate chinese start_e7de7aa9:

    # doc "Oh. Well, Nurse, uh..."
    doc "哦。好吧，额，是护士……"

# game/script.rpy:790
translate chinese start_405bd2ec:

    # "He snaps his fingers, trying to remember."
    "他打了个响指，试图回忆起来。"

# game/script.rpy:792
translate chinese start_9336fdbb:

    # j "...Anna?"
    j "……安娜？"

# game/script.rpy:794
translate chinese start_ccd6c5f4:

    # doc "Nurse Anna. That’s the one."
    doc "护士安娜。就是她。"

# game/script.rpy:795
translate chinese start_d4939b64:

    # doc "She told me."
    doc "她告诉我的。"

# game/script.rpy:796
translate chinese start_f13b6296:

    # doc "And yes, I know about you two. No need to act surprised."
    doc "还有是的，我知道你们俩的事。没必要装模作样地惊讶。"

# game/script.rpy:797
translate chinese start_693fa8e4:

    # doc "You’re a lucky guy, you know that?"
    doc "你挺幸运的，知道吗？"

# game/script.rpy:799
translate chinese start_984f6b91_2:

    # j "...Yeah."
    j "……是啊。"

# game/script.rpy:801
translate chinese start_e34681d6:

    # doc "When I first found out, I was against letting her care for you—being objective and all that stuff, you know?—but she really wanted to. So I thought, whatever."
    doc "在我刚发现这事的时候，我反对让她照顾你。只是从客观方面来说，你懂吗？ 但她真的很想照顾你。所以我想，无所谓了。"

# game/script.rpy:802
translate chinese start_94e450d3:

    # doc "And she’s taking it well, so it’s okay, I guess..."
    doc "而她也照顾的不错，所以应该没事，大概吧……"

# game/script.rpy:812
translate chinese start_8691294f:

    # "The doctor stares off into space, then looks at me and grins."
    "医生凝视着别处，然后对着我咧嘴一笑。"

# game/script.rpy:814
translate chinese start_6cb89d9f:

    # doc "Oh, I see."
    doc "哦，我明白了。"

# game/script.rpy:815
translate chinese start_0aab2a62:

    # doc "It’s her."
    doc "是因为她吧。"

# game/script.rpy:817
translate chinese start_a475dd4c_1:

    # j "What?"
    j "什么？"

# game/script.rpy:819
translate chinese start_d9c47771:

    # doc "She’s the reason you want to get the hell out of here, huh?"
    doc "她才是你疯狂想要逃离这里的原因，对吧？"

# game/script.rpy:820
translate chinese start_e954c9c6:

    # doc "I don’t blame you. There’s no privacy here at all."
    doc "我不怪你。毕竟你在这里毫无隐私可言。"

# game/script.rpy:822
translate chinese start_d9dc9fc2:

    # j "Oh, no, I didn’t—"
    j "哦，不是，我没有——"

# game/script.rpy:824
translate chinese start_158d707c:

    # doc "Don’t be ashamed, now. I get what it’s like."
    doc "现在不必感到羞耻。我知道那是一种什么样的感受。"

# game/script.rpy:826
translate chinese start_61751b43:

    # "He drops the smile."
    "他收起微笑。"

# game/script.rpy:828
translate chinese start_e36bde29:

    # doc "But you can’t be thinking of those sorts of things. You’ve got to rest properly."
    doc "但你不能胡思乱想。你必须好好休息。"

# game/script.rpy:829
translate chinese start_d78cbe60:

    # doc "All right? All right."
    doc "这样就行了吧？就这样了。"

# game/script.rpy:835
translate chinese start_9b411f0b:

    # "He leaves with a thumbs-up."
    "他对我竖了个大拇指然后就走了。"

# game/script.rpy:836
translate chinese start_270cf170:

    # "Two of the other patients are laughing and whistling, and another one is grumbling with what must be jealousy."
    "另外两个病人边大笑边吹口哨。还有一个在抱怨，一定是嫉妒了。"

# game/script.rpy:837
translate chinese start_9d74d319:

    # "Idiots."
    "一群蠢货。"

# game/script.rpy:838
translate chinese start_88c15fd5:

    # "My journal is pressed up against me, in a new hiding spot—I’ve moved it three times now."
    "我的日记被我紧紧抱在胸前，藏在一个新的地方——我已经把它转移了三次。"

# game/script.rpy:839
translate chinese start_d39a004c:

    # "I’ve got to write in it."
    "我必须写点什么。"

# game/script.rpy:840
translate chinese start_d58f4639:

    # "My thoughts are burning a hole in my skull. I've got to share them with someone, even if that someone is a piece of paper."
    "我的思绪快要烧穿我的大脑。我必须找个人分享它们，哪怕这个人只是张白纸。"

# game/script.rpy:841
translate chinese start_404df35a:

    # "But not now. She’s still out there somewhere."
    "但不是现在。她还在附近。"

# game/script.rpy:851
translate chinese start_94d16b5e:

    # n "August 6"
    n "8月6日"

# game/script.rpy:852
translate chinese start_3f1e7285:

    # n "Damn it. God damn it all."
    n "见鬼。真见鬼。"

# game/script.rpy:853
translate chinese start_38282ca3:

    # n "I’m stuck here with nothing to do but lie uselessly and {i}wait.{/i}"
    n "我被困在这里无事可做，只能一无所用地躺着{i}等待{/i}。"

