translate chinese start_c1ebc916_4:

    # n "Wait"
    n "等待"

# game/script.rpy:873
translate chinese start_9ebdef62:

    # n "For how long?"
    n "究竟要等多久？"

# game/script.rpy:877
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_9:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:885
translate chinese start_926e39aa:

    # "It’s two hours after I’ve written down those words."
    "我写下这些文字后又过了两个小时。"

# game/script.rpy:886
translate chinese start_9c90b8de:

    # "I'm looking at the little notebook that is my journal. I've got it in my hands."
    "我看着这本小小的记事本，我的日记本。我把它握在手中。"

# game/script.rpy:887
translate chinese start_de9d074c:

    # "I am amazingly lucky to have it."
    "我何其幸运能拥有它。"

# game/script.rpy:888
translate chinese start_2429ad53:

    # "Someone had left both the notebook and a pen in the nightstand next to my bed. I checked the nightstand's drawers on a whim, and there they were."
    "有人在我枕边的床头柜里留下了记事本和一支笔。我心血来潮打开了床头柜的抽屉，发现了它们。"

# game/script.rpy:889
translate chinese start_f31629b9:

    # "Now they’re the only things keeping me sane—there's no TV or books or even magazines in here."
    "如今它们是唯一能让我保持清醒的东西——这里没有电视，也没有书，更别提杂志了。"

# game/script.rpy:890
translate chinese start_92652ef0:

    # "I’m counting the pages I've got left in the notebook, checking how much ink there is in my pen."
    "我数了数记事本剩下的页数，看看笔里还剩下多少墨水。"

# game/script.rpy:899
translate chinese start_f814ec1c:

    # "Then {i}she{/i} comes in, and I feel my heart stop."
    "然后{i}她{/i}进来了，我心脏骤停。"

# game/script.rpy:911
translate chinese start_48fa674c:

    # a "Good evening, boys."
    a "晚上好，孩子们。"

# game/script.rpy:917
translate chinese start_b4c721e6:

    # "She greets everyone, but she’s only looking at me."
    "她问候了所有人，但独独只看向我。"

# game/script.rpy:918
translate chinese start_01099520:

    # "I murmur back a hello."
    "我嗫嚅着回打了个招呼。"

# game/script.rpy:919
translate chinese start_4399cb28:

    # "Meanwhile my hands are still holding the notebook."
    "此时，我的手仍然握着日记本。"

# game/script.rpy:920
translate chinese start_be641802:

    # "Clutching it, actually."
    "准确地说，是紧紧抓住它。"

# game/script.rpy:921
translate chinese start_96f06902:

    # "I can feel beads of sweat forming on my forehead."
    "我能感觉到我的额头上渗出了汗珠。"

# game/script.rpy:922
translate chinese start_1920a2dd:

    # "The notebook is small. Very small—my hands must be hiding it from view. Or are they?"
    "日记本小小一个。非常小——我的双手一定把它遮住了。是吗？"

# game/script.rpy:926
translate chinese start_04c6ec73:

    # "If she’s noticed, Anna pays it no mind. She wheels in the cart with our medication."
    "如果安娜注意到了，她也不会多想什么。她推着推车，上面放着我们的药。"

# game/script.rpy:927
translate chinese start_71fe5437:

    # "While she’s busy with the other patients, I slip the notebook and pen under my blanket, smooth it over, and lie quietly."
    "正当她忙着照顾其他病人时，我把日记本和笔藏到毯子下压平，静静地躺着。"

# game/script.rpy:938
translate chinese start_7ad2bac4:

    # a "How are you holding up, sweetie?"
    a "你还好吗，亲爱的？"

# game/script.rpy:943
translate chinese start_47267f9f:

    # "I nearly jump at Anna’s whispered words. I didn’t notice her approach."
    "安娜的低语在耳边响起，我差点跳起来。我都没注意到她过来了。"

# game/script.rpy:945
translate chinese start_760ddd8e:

    # j "Fine. I’m fine... thanks."
    j "很好。我很好……谢谢。"

# game/script.rpy:951
translate chinese start_559b7537:

    # a "Hmm..."
    a "嗯……"

# game/script.rpy:957
translate chinese start_2b230a8c:

    # a "Jack, don’t you remember what I told you?"
    a "杰克，你忘了我跟你说过什么吗？"

# game/script.rpy:963
translate chinese start_bb0436d4:

    # a "It’s no good putting on a brave face. I’m here for you, okay?"
    a "你不必故作勇敢。我就在你身边，好吗？"

# game/script.rpy:965
translate chinese start_4cdb7743:

    # j "...What’s this about?"
    j "……这是什么意思？"

# game/script.rpy:967
translate chinese start_07a37042:

    # "{i}Does she know?{/i}"
    "{i}她知道了吗？{/i}"

# game/script.rpy:973
translate chinese start_d2b982c9:

    # a "I know about everything, you see."
    a "我知道一切，你瞧。"

# game/script.rpy:978
translate chinese start_c634edb4:

    # "She leans in closer. I nearly faint."
    "她靠得更近了。我差点晕过去。"

# game/script.rpy:984
translate chinese start_d6109f9d:

    # a "Everything."
    a "一切。"

# game/script.rpy:986
translate chinese start_c9241255:

    # j "Y-Yeah?"
    j "是…是吗？"

# game/script.rpy:991
translate chinese start_210c06eb:

    # a "Yes."
    a "是的。"

# game/script.rpy:996
translate chinese start_d0b70009:

    # a "I had a little chat with your doctor, you know?"
    a "我和你的主治医生聊了一会儿，你知道吗？"

# game/script.rpy:1001
translate chinese start_ca7074d0:

    # a "And he told me a~ll about how much trouble you’re having. Down {i}there.{/i}"
    a "他把你的问题全～部都告诉我了。下面的{i}问题{/i}。"

# game/script.rpy:1006
translate chinese start_1fa4d16a:

    # "As soon as I realize what she means, my tense body loosens up."
    "我听懂了她话里的意思，紧张的身体便放松下来。"

# game/script.rpy:1008
translate chinese start_d7990730:

    # j "Ah, yeah. That."
    j "啊，对。那个。"

# game/script.rpy:1009
translate chinese start_8c572295:

    # j "It’s, uh... a bit of a problem, I guess."
    j "确实，呃……有点问题，我猜。"

# game/script.rpy:1017
translate chinese start_06ebcf12:

    # a "Oh, sweetie."
    a "噢，亲爱的。"

# game/script.rpy:1022
translate chinese start_180318df:

    # a "Well, I’m sorry. Your health has priority over sex."
    a "啊，我很抱歉。比起生理需求，你的健康才是头等大事。"

# game/script.rpy:1027
translate chinese start_f8edb93d:

    # a "But don’t you worry. I’m not going anywhere."
    a "但你别担心，我哪里都不会去。"

# game/script.rpy:1032
translate chinese start_f9140c50:

    # "She puts her hand on my blanket, starts smoothing it out absentmindedly."
    "她把手放在我的毯子上，开始心不在焉地把它抚平。"

# game/script.rpy:1038
translate chinese start_de49417b:

    # a "It makes me happy, though. To see you like this again."
    a "不过，能再次见到你，我很开心。"

# game/script.rpy:1043
translate chinese start_274d9d4a:

    # a "After how you acted before your accident, I thought..."
    a "看你出事前的一举一动，我以为……"

# game/script.rpy:1049
translate chinese start_0fb579b3:

    # a "...Never mind."
    a "……没什么。"

# game/script.rpy:1057
translate chinese start_9329f2ab:

    # "Without warning, she leans in even closer."
    "猝不及防，她靠得更近了。"

# game/script.rpy:1058
translate chinese start_95829710:

    # "I feel her hot breath on my cheek."
    "我感觉到她炽热的呼吸扑在我的脸颊上。"

# game/script.rpy:1064
translate chinese start_bafabe7d:

    # a "But since you’re so eager, Jack, I promise that after you’re released I’ll give you the time of your life."
    a "不过既然你这么想要，杰克，我向你保证，等你康复之后我会补偿你的。"

# game/script.rpy:1070
translate chinese start_17ab2f48:

    # a "I’ll make you finally forget a~ll about {i}Grace.{/i}"
    a "我会让你忘掉{i}格瑞丝{/i}的全～部。"

# game/script.rpy:1072
translate chinese start_1eb22674:

    # "Her words are like a slap in the face. I can only stare back."
    "她的话仿佛一记耳光扇在我的脸上。我只能呆呆地看向她。"

# game/script.rpy:1079
translate chinese start_e9a4fbf2:

    # a "Hmm... So you still care about her."
    a "嗯……原来你还在意着她。"

# game/script.rpy:1086
translate chinese start_d650c9d1:

    # a "I don’t like that."
    a "我不喜欢这样。"

# game/script.rpy:1091
translate chinese start_0671775b:

    # a "Someone like you and someone like her... You never should’ve been together in the first place."
    a "像你这样的人和像她那样的人……你们从一开始就不应该在一起。"

# game/script.rpy:1097
translate chinese start_8ac89fe1:

    # a "Please think only of me."
    a "拜托，只想着我一个人就好。"

# game/script.rpy:1103
translate chinese start_5343770e:

    # a "After all, we were made for each other."
    a "毕竟，我们是为彼此而存在的。"

# game/script.rpy:1105
translate chinese start_6441704a:

    # j "If I do... If I promise I’ll be with you, always..."
    j "如果我真的……如果我保证我会陪着你，生生世世……"

# game/script.rpy:1106
translate chinese start_d07c02b5:

    # j "...will you leave Grace out of this?"
    j "……你会离开格瑞丝吗？"

# game/script.rpy:1113
translate chinese start_538881e6:

    # a "No, that’s no good."
    a "不，这样不好。"

# game/script.rpy:1120
translate chinese start_8ef98cf0:

    # a "I can’t do that."
    a "我做不到。"

# game/script.rpy:1126
translate chinese start_941fae57:

    # a "Just your asking that... it shows you’re still thinking about her."
    a "你都这么问了……说明你还对她念念不忘。"

# game/script.rpy:1128
translate chinese start_0dd93cea:

    # j "She hasn’t got anything to do with this!"
    j "她和这件事没有任何关系！"

# game/script.rpy:1129
translate chinese start_444ea1c8:

    # j "With what you did to me, and what..."
    j "不论你对我做了什么，还有……"

# game/script.rpy:1131
translate chinese start_b561aab6:

    # "{i}...and what I’ll do to you.{/i}"
    "{i}……还有不论我将会对你做什么。{/i}"

# game/script.rpy:1133
translate chinese start_b2ddad4b:

    # j "So leave her out of it. Are you holding her somewhere?"
    j "所以别把她扯进来。你把她藏在哪了？"

# game/script.rpy:1138
translate chinese start_0373aee9:

    # a "Ah, at least that girl’s good for one thing."
    a "啊哈，至少那女孩还有点用处。"

# game/script.rpy:1144
translate chinese start_ae3721f1:

    # a "Thanks to her you’ve been a good boy, even though you’re still so confused."
    a "多亏了她，你表现还不错，尽管你仍然魂不守舍。"

# game/script.rpy:1146
translate chinese start_e872fba7:

    # j "Anna, {i}please.{/i}"
    j "安娜，{i}求你了{/i}。"

# game/script.rpy:1148
translate chinese start_405eb5b2:

    # "I'm close to crying."
    "我快要哭了。"

# game/script.rpy:1149
translate chinese start_fafe151f:

    # "I want to tear my hair out."
    "我想扯我的头发。"

# game/script.rpy:1154
translate chinese start_b4b8de49:

    # "Anna smiles again."
    "安娜又笑了。"

# game/script.rpy:1160
translate chinese start_40fc565d:

    # a "Fine, sweetie. I’ll promise I won’t hurt her."
    a "好吧，亲爱的。我向你保证我不会伤害她的。"

# game/script.rpy:1165
translate chinese start_72e3b87e:

    # a "As long as you do one thing for me."
    a "只要你为我做一件事。"

# game/script.rpy:1172
translate chinese start_3c43ae5b:

    # a "Do you know what that is?"
    a "你知道是什么事吗？"

# game/script.rpy:1174
translate chinese start_ab928408:

    # j "...I do."
    j "……我知道。"

# game/script.rpy:1176
translate chinese start_bd7e173e:

    # "Of course I do. It’s something she’s been telling me to do for ages—since before I got here."
    "我当然知道。是她多年来一直叫我做的事——自从我来到这之前就开始了。"

# game/script.rpy:1177
translate chinese start_9b9d5a2f:

    # "She’s like a broken record."
    "她就像一张坏掉的唱片。"

# game/script.rpy:1179
translate chinese start_67eb7911:

    # j "You want me to remember everything."
    j "你想让我记起所有事。"

# game/script.rpy:1186
translate chinese start_fdc5b7df:

    # a "Yep."
    a "是的。"

# game/script.rpy:1192
translate chinese start_d7b51f9a:

    # a "Oh, I can’t wait."
    a "噢，我等不及了。"

# game/script.rpy:1198
translate chinese start_1aeb7718:

    # a "When you do that, everything will be {i}perfect.{/i}"
    a "等你记起来了，一切都会{i}完美如初{/i}。"

# game/script.rpy:1204
translate chinese start_da979759:

    # a "We’ll be together again. Forever."
    a "我们会重归于好。永远也不分开。"

# game/script.rpy:1209
translate chinese start_c0e7de37:

    # a "So promise you’ll remember."
    a "所以向我保证你会想起来。"

# game/script.rpy:1211
translate chinese start_b9cd904b:

    # j "I promise I’ll try."
    j "我答应你我会试试的。"

# game/script.rpy:1220
translate chinese start_9a58adc6:

    # a "No."
    a "不。"

# game/script.rpy:1225
translate chinese start_d29606be:

    # a "That’s not good enough."
    a "那还不够。"

# game/script.rpy:1230
translate chinese start_c35e51b7:

    # a "You promised you’d try before, and look where that got us."
    a "你之前答应过你会试试，但看看我们现在落到什么地步了。"

# game/script.rpy:1235
translate chinese start_72e151e4:

    # a "Tell me you’ll {i}do it.{/i}"
    a "告诉我你会{i}想起来{/i}。"

# game/script.rpy:1239
translate chinese start_8ee95afa:

    # j "I—I promise."
    j "我——我会的。"

# game/script.rpy:1240
translate chinese start_763ee4d1:

    # j "I’ll recall it all."
    j "我会全部想起来的。"

# game/script.rpy:1247
translate chinese start_ef85c08c:

    # a "Good."
    a "很好。"

# game/script.rpy:1253
translate chinese start_e68a163c:

    # a "We'll work on that when you get out of here, but..."
    a "到你离开时我们会成功的，不过……"

# game/script.rpy:1259
translate chinese start_fd047a84:

    # a "...if your memory comes back to you before then, tell me before you tell anyone else."
    a "……如果在此之前你恢复了记忆，第一个就要告诉我。"

# game/script.rpy:1264
translate chinese start_082fe3c4:

    # a "Okay?"
    a "好吗？"

# game/script.rpy:1270
translate chinese start_85821f33:

    # a "Bye-bye for now."
    a "我先走了。"

# game/script.rpy:1275
translate chinese start_c5fac421:

    # "She wheels out the cart, glancing back one last time with that eerie look of hers."
    "她推着推车，表情阴森地回头看了最后一眼。"

# game/script.rpy:1277
translate chinese start_4869d387:

    # "I can’t tell her I already remember."
    "我不能告诉她我已经都想起来了。"

# game/script.rpy:1278
translate chinese start_2742cf2c:

    # "I've known since before my injury."
    "在我受伤之前我就知道了。"

# game/script.rpy:1279
translate chinese start_17cf460a:

    # "I’ve known that, when we were both children... she..."
    "我知道，我们还是小孩子的时候……她……"

# game/script.rpy:1280
translate chinese start_8b7ca183:

    # "No, I can’t tell her."
    "不，我不能告诉她。"

# game/script.rpy:1281
translate chinese start_30ab74a1:

    # "If I do that, she wins, and Grace dies."
    "如果我告诉她，她就赢了，格瑞丝会死的。"

# game/script.rpy:1282
translate chinese start_edc10a24:

    # "And maybe I die, too."
    "我也可能会死。"

# game/script.rpy:1283
translate chinese start_a406e8b9:

    # "I can’t win by playing along with Anna’s delusions."
    "配合安娜的幻想演戏是赢不了的。"

# game/script.rpy:1307
translate chinese start_122e8d98:

    # n "August 7"
    n "8月7日"

# game/script.rpy:1313
translate chinese start_dc4d56b4:

    # n "I can’t just sit here waiting."
    n "我不能坐以待毙。"

# game/script.rpy:1320
translate chinese start_50aa040a:

    # n "I've got to wait, and I {i}will{/i}, but I feel like I can’t wait, either."
    n "我不得不等待，我{i}会{/i}的，但我觉得我也等不及了。"

# game/script.rpy:1322
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_10:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:1327
translate chinese start_63ff1c6d:

    # n "I'm doing nothing, and it's eating me up."
    n "我什么都做不了，我正在被蚕食。"

# game/script.rpy:1334
translate chinese start_feab3fe0:

    # n "If a stomach is empty long enough, it starts eating itself."
    n "如果胃长时间都空空如也，它会开始以自己为食。"

# game/script.rpy:1339
translate chinese start_fc1be541:

    # n "Do you know that?"
    n "你知道吗？"

# game/script.rpy:1344
translate chinese start_80e48241:

    # n "I know that."
    n "我知道的。"

# game/script.rpy:1346
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_11:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:1353
translate chinese start_72f818e5:

    # n "If I don't do something right now, I'm afraid I might go crazy."
    n "如果我不立马采取行动，我恐怕会疯掉。"

# game/script.rpy:1355
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_12:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:1368
translate chinese start_06aa4bdb:

    # n "I'm going to write down everything that happened."
    n "我要把发生的一切都写下来。"

# game/script.rpy:1369
translate chinese start_9f746d21:

    # n "Maybe that’ll help me make sense of things."
    n "也许这能帮助我理解事情。"

# game/script.rpy:1370
translate chinese start_2d1ac3e4:

    # n "Right now, my thoughts are buzzing together in my mind like flies around a turd."
    n "此刻，我的思绪在脑海中盘旋翻腾，就像一群苍蝇围着粪便嗡嗡作响一样。"

# game/script.rpy:1372
translate chinese start_1ffe3714:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I want my mind to be clear."
    nvl clear
    n "我想要理清我的思绪。"

# game/script.rpy:1375
translate chinese start_807a8675:

    # n "To do what I'm going to do, and to do it properly, my mind needs to be clear."
    n "为了做我要做的事，为了顺利完成它，我必须保持头脑清醒。"

# game/script.rpy:1376
translate chinese start_b4468ef2:

    # n "Unclouded."
    n "思维清晰。"

# game/script.rpy:1378
translate chinese start_b2f55806:

    # nvl clear
    # n "This notebook is small, but I think I've got enough space to write everything down."
    nvl clear
    n "日记本很小，但我觉得我有足够的篇幅能记下一切。"

# game/script.rpy:1381
translate chinese start_49270a34:

    # n "It's not a long story."
    n "故事并不冗长。"

# game/script.rpy:1383
translate chinese start_4246300d:

    # nvl clear
    # n "So here it goes. Everything."
    nvl clear
    n "那么开始吧。写下一切。"

# game/script.rpy:1387
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_13:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:1401
translate chinese start_cf7c8050:

    # n "I met Anna—met her {i}again{/i} after so many years—in the store where I worked."
    n "我在我工作的店里遇见了安娜，时隔多年后{i}再次{/i} 遇见了她。"

# game/script.rpy:1402
translate chinese start_858c6b9c:

    # n "Grace wasn’t there at the time."
    n "那时格瑞丝不在。"

# game/script.rpy:1403
translate chinese start_0451d921:

    # n "It wasn't a coincidence that Anna visited the store when she did."
    n "在她不在的时候安娜光顾了这家店，这并非巧合。"

# game/script.rpy:1404
translate chinese start_a8c0963a:

    # n "It couldn't have been."
    n "不可能那么凑巧。"

# game/script.rpy:1405
translate chinese start_cca57995:

    # n "She must've been following me."
    n "她一定是在跟踪我。"

# game/script.rpy:1409
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_14:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:1418
translate chinese start_5c134ac1:

    # "The first time she came in, I was at the cash register."
    "她第一次进店时，我在收银台。"

# game/script.rpy:1423
translate chinese start_c1178953:

    # "She walked straight up to me, cutting in line."
    "她径直走向我，插了队。"

# game/script.rpy:1424
translate chinese start_0bf9d115:

    # "An old woman was busy counting her change, and didn’t complain. Nobody else complained, either."
    "一个老太太正忙着数零钱，没说什么。其他人也一言不发。"

# game/script.rpy:1425
translate chinese start_ec474799:

    # "Anna stood there a while, staring at me."
    "安娜定在那里，盯着我。"

# game/script.rpy:1429
translate chinese start_028d4863:

    # "Then she said—"
    "接着她开口了——"

# game/script.rpy:1436
translate chinese start_82bb9a08:

    # n "No."
    n "不。"

# game/script.rpy:1437
translate chinese start_52f9cfa0:

    # n "No, I can’t do this."
    n "不，我做不到。"

# game/script.rpy:1438
translate chinese start_ae8a6d07:

    # n "I can’t start here."
    n "我没法从这里开始。"

# game/script.rpy:1439
translate chinese start_632af28c:

    # n "I can’t do it."
    n "我做不到。"

# game/script.rpy:1440
translate chinese start_003b199f:

    # n "There’s already too much of that woman in my life."
    n "那个女人在我生命中已经占据了太多篇幅。"

# game/script.rpy:1442
translate chinese start_9c9c2e43:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I've got to start with someone else."
    nvl clear
    n "我得从其他人入手。"

# game/script.rpy:1445
translate chinese start_bc342fad:

    # n "Someone I miss."
    n "一个我心心念念的人。"

# game/script.rpy:1446
translate chinese start_24c9dc53:

    # n "Grace."
    n "格瑞丝。"

# game/script.rpy:1448
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_15:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:1461
translate chinese start_e2e0d0c1:

    # n "Grace was a girl who worked at the same store I worked at."
    n "格瑞丝和我在同一家店工作。"

# game/script.rpy:1462
translate chinese start_f4f96e6d:

    # n "She was—and is, still is—a kind, sweet girl."
    n "那时，她是一个善良可爱的女生，现在也依然是。"

# game/script.rpy:1463
translate chinese start_b1057598:

    # n "She's a little quiet. But that's perfectly fine."
    n "她有点安静。但这完全没问题。"

# game/script.rpy:1465
translate chinese start_9d0f8a94:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I hated her."
    nvl clear
    n "我讨厌她。"

# game/script.rpy:1468
translate chinese start_65252025:

    # n "I hated most people."
    n "我讨厌大多数人。"

# game/script.rpy:1469
translate chinese start_05e6ef63:

    # n "And most things."
    n "也讨厌大多数东西。"

# game/script.rpy:1470
translate chinese start_22d8b7c9:

    # n "I was a real asshole."
    n "我是个不折不扣的混蛋。"

# game/script.rpy:1472
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_16:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:1486
translate chinese start_e8a54e08:

    # n "I didn’t spend time with other people."
    n "我不会和其他人相处。"

# game/script.rpy:1487
translate chinese start_5c29b22a:

    # n "Whenever a coworker invited me somewhere, I’d turn them down."
    n "每次同事邀请我去哪，我都一口回绝。"

# game/script.rpy:1488
translate chinese start_90dfc09c:

    # n "I didn’t chat with anyone during breaks, either."
    n "休息时我也不会和任何人闲聊。"

# game/script.rpy:1489
translate chinese start_43ed7f24:

    # n "It was just how I was—how I'd always been."
    n "我就是这样的人——历来如此。"

# game/script.rpy:1491
translate chinese start_dede59e8:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I avoided Grace, too, of course."
    nvl clear
    n "当然，我也避开了格瑞丝。"

# game/script.rpy:1494
translate chinese start_f12992bb:

    # n "She tried to talk to me a few times, but then I started avoiding her even more."
    n "有几次她试图和我找话聊，但之后我变得更加躲着她。"

# game/script.rpy:1496
translate chinese start_d6669ce0:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I only took shifts I thought she wouldn’t take."
    nvl clear
    n "我只会在她不在时才去轮班。"

# game/script.rpy:1499
translate chinese start_33f8e58e:

    # n "The times we still ended up working together, I stayed as far away from her as I could."
    n "我们还一起工作时，我都尽可能离她远远的。"

# game/script.rpy:1500
translate chinese start_02b9f97b:

    # n "It worked, for a while."
    n "这种方法奏效了一段时间。"

# game/script.rpy:1501
translate chinese start_22e6a1b1:

    # n "Then came the day we talked—really talked—for the first time."
    n "然后有一天我们谈话了，发自肺腑的那种，这是我们的第一次谈话。"

# game/script.rpy:1503
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_17:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:1520
translate chinese start_5989f172:

    # "I was restocking the shelves alongside an old, greasy, long-haired man when Grace came along."
    "我正在和一个油腻的长发老男人一起补货时，格瑞丝来了。"

# game/script.rpy:1527
translate chinese start_c5ea5d85:

    # "I didn’t even look at her."
    "我看都没看她。"

# game/script.rpy:1528
translate chinese start_bd2b2dca:

    # "Instead I became very interested in stacking cans of food onto the lower shelves."
    "我对堆放在低层货架上的罐头食品来了兴趣。"

# game/script.rpy:1529
translate chinese start_33bba6a4:

    # "I waited for her to leave."
    "我等着她离开。"

# game/script.rpy:1546
translate chinese start_c11f6ab0:

    # g "Um, Don, you can switch with me, all right?"
    g "啊，唐，我和你换换吧，好吗？"

# game/script.rpy:1550
translate chinese start_11c7bf26:

    # g "You can go help Susie. I already did the bottom shelves there."
    g "你去帮苏茜吧。那边的最底层货架我已经整理好了。"

# game/script.rpy:1552
translate chinese start_c146ecf8:

    # "Don, the old man, thanked her and left."
    "唐，也就是和我一起的老男人，谢过她之后离开了。"

# game/script.rpy:1559
translate chinese start_b4b0c66e:

    # "...And Grace started working next to me."
    "……于是格瑞丝在我旁边开始工作。"

# game/script.rpy:1563
translate chinese start_d0768f02:

    # "A minute went by."
    "一分钟过后。"

# game/script.rpy:1564
translate chinese start_423802e4:

    # "I found that I couldn’t work in peace. Just her being there made me upset."
    "我发现自己无法静下心来工作。就因为她在这儿，我心烦意乱。"

# game/script.rpy:1565
translate chinese start_557ad684:

    # "I had to say something."
    "我必须说点什么。"

# game/script.rpy:1567
translate chinese start_7f874f7f:

    # j "I’m fine on my own."
    j "我自己一个人可以的。"

# game/script.rpy:1574
translate chinese start_396bd16f:

    # g "Hm?"
    g "嗯？"

# game/script.rpy:1576
translate chinese start_076d19f0:

    # j "If you want to take a break or something, you can. I’m fine on my own."
    j "如果你想休息一下什么的，你去吧。我自己一个人没问题。"

# game/script.rpy:1580
translate chinese start_32825efb:

    # g "Oh, no, I don’t mind doing this."
    g "哦，不用了，我不介意做这个。"

# game/script.rpy:1582
translate chinese start_e7eb75b9:

    # j "I see."
    j "好吧。"

# game/script.rpy:1584
translate chinese start_2b107a6d:

    # "{i}Can’t she take a hint?{/i} I thought then."
    "{i}她没领会我的意思吗？{/i}我当时想。"

# game/script.rpy:1588
translate chinese start_8e945f90:

    # g "It’s, um, it’s his back, you know?"
    g "是，呃，是因为他的背，你知道吗？"

# game/script.rpy:1590
translate chinese start_a475dd4c_2:

    # j "What?"
    j "啥？"

# game/script.rpy:1596
translate chinese start_dab13e7a:

    # g "Don’s back hurts a lot. So I asked him to switch."
    g "唐的背很痛。所以我和他换了。"

# game/script.rpy:1598
translate chinese start_adf9d9e7:

    # j "Oh, I see."
    j "噢，我懂了。"

# game/script.rpy:1604
translate chinese start_8d0c0a92:

    # g "He has trouble with the lower shelves, so..."
    g "他整理低层货架会很吃力，所以……"

# game/script.rpy:1606
translate chinese start_115945b2:

    # j "I get it."
    j "我知道了。"

# game/script.rpy:1612
translate chinese start_22d6aae2:

    # g "I didn’t do it to bother you, I swear."
    g "我不是想要打扰你，我发誓。"

# game/script.rpy:1614
translate chinese start_3d9a3bc5:

    # j "I said I get it."
    j "我说我知道了。"

# game/script.rpy:1620
translate chinese start_b2c974f4:

    # g "Okay..."
    g "好……"

# game/script.rpy:1624
translate chinese start_b770dfe1:

    # "We went on restocking in silence."
    "我们又陷入沉默，继续补货。"

# game/script.rpy:1625
translate chinese start_ba6d5917:

    # "...For about another minute."
    "……大约又过了一分钟。"

# game/script.rpy:1634
translate chinese start_347a6aaf:

    # g "Um..."
    g "呃……"

# game/script.rpy:1641
translate chinese start_6a0edcf1:

    # g "...I know you don’t like me very much, so I thought you might think I was..."
    g "……我知道你不是很喜欢我，所以我以为你可能会觉得我……"

# game/script.rpy:1645
translate chinese start_a626afe9:

    # g "...bothering you on purpose."
    g "……是在故意干扰你。"

# game/script.rpy:1649
translate chinese start_969c82c9:

    # g "So I’m sorry."
    g "我很抱歉。"

# game/script.rpy:1651
translate chinese start_2c34ed1a:

    # "I sighed."
    "我叹了口气。"

# game/script.rpy:1653
translate chinese start_80d27382:

    # j "Who says I don’t like you?"
    j "谁说的我不喜欢你？"

# game/script.rpy:1659
translate chinese start_0297fa45:

    # g "Huh?"
    g "哈？"

# game/script.rpy:1663
translate chinese start_044829ec:

    # g "Don’t you?"
    g "不是吗？"

# game/script.rpy:1669
translate chinese start_65cd36ff:

    # g "You’re always... avoiding me."
    g "你总是……躲着我。"

# game/script.rpy:1671
translate chinese start_59496966:

    # j "Yeah, don’t take that personally."
    j "是的，别放在心上。"

# game/script.rpy:1672
translate chinese start_24c463c0:

    # j "That’s just how I am."
    j "我的个性就是这样。"

# game/script.rpy:1673
translate chinese start_8f981387:

    # j "I don’t care about other people."
    j "我不在乎其他人。"

# game/script.rpy:1675
translate chinese start_5fce3056:

    # "...Fucking dumbass."
    "……真他妈蠢。"

# game/script.rpy:1676
translate chinese start_26f38a1a:

    # "If I could go back in time and punch myself in the mouth, I would."
    "如果我能回到过去，我真的会给我自己几拳。"

# game/script.rpy:1684
translate chinese start_42968b3a:

    # g "So you like me?"
    g "所以你喜欢我咯？"

# game/script.rpy:1686
translate chinese start_01a8fa9a:

    # j "What? No, I didn’t say that."
    j "啥？不，我可没说。"

# game/script.rpy:1687
translate chinese start_cac77300:

    # j "Get a clue."
    j "懂了。"

# game/script.rpy:1694
translate chinese start_fbdd5be7:

    # g "Haha! Just kidding~"
    g "哈哈！开个玩笑啦～"

# game/script.rpy:1700
translate chinese start_a4f5f359:

    # n "We didn’t talk for the rest of the day, so I thought that was that."
    n "之后那天我们都没再说话，所以我觉得我俩就这样了。"

# game/script.rpy:1701
translate chinese start_e573fd6f:

    # n "{i}She’ll leave me alone{/i}, I thought, {i}now that she knows I prefer it that way.{/i}"
    n "{i}她不会再打扰我了{/i}，我想，{i}既然她已经知道我喜欢一个人呆着。{/i}"

# game/script.rpy:1702
translate chinese start_b7f6b224:

    # n "But she didn’t."
    n "但是她没有。"

# game/script.rpy:1704
translate chinese start_6731381d:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I've always thanked my lucky stars that she didn't leave me alone after that."
    nvl clear
    n "在那之后格瑞丝并没有远离我，为此我一直对上天的眷顾感激不尽。"

# game/script.rpy:1707
translate chinese start_477a7764:

    # n "Maybe she should have, though."
    n "不过，也许她还是不应该接近我。"

# game/script.rpy:1708
translate chinese start_05099d59:

    # n "For her own sake."
    n "为她自己好。"

# game/script.rpy:1710
translate chinese start_2996dfe4:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I hope she can forgive me."
    nvl clear
    n "我希望她能原谅我。"

# game/script.rpy:1714
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_18:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:1728
translate chinese start_a6259ffd:

    # n "Writing about the past has been a good idea."
    n "写下往事是个不错的点子。"

# game/script.rpy:1729
translate chinese start_3a32ea17:

    # n "Right now it doesn’t even bother me where I am, who I’m with."
    n "如今我身处何地、和谁一起都无所谓了。"

# game/script.rpy:1730
translate chinese start_8045061e:

    # n "And thinking of Grace, remembering the way she smiled, is giving me courage."
    n "一想到格瑞丝，想起她的笑容，我就充满了勇气。"

# game/script.rpy:1731
translate chinese start_19617e3b:

    # n "She got hurt because of me, so I will do anything to make her happy and safe."
    n "她因我而受到伤害，因此我会不顾一切确保她安然无恙，给予她幸福。"

# game/script.rpy:1733
translate chinese start_14da90fb:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{w=1}The weather was nice out today."
    nvl clear
    n "{w=1}今天外面天气很好。"

# game/script.rpy:1736
translate chinese start_2fce67af:

    # n "The sky was blue."
    n "天空蔚蓝。"

# game/script.rpy:1737
translate chinese start_6de358f9:

    # n "There is a tiny window on the wall to my left."
    n "我左边的墙上有一扇小小的窗户。"

# game/script.rpy:1738
translate chinese start_f183bf02:

    # n "I can look through it if I twist my head around."
    n "我扭过头，就能从这扇窗远眺。"

# game/script.rpy:1740
translate chinese start_3aeaed1b:

    # nvl clear
    # n "That small patch of the sky is the only beautiful thing around here."
    nvl clear
    n "那小小一隅的天空，是这里仅存的美丽事物。"

# game/script.rpy:1743
translate chinese start_d3dec9ad:

    # n "That and my memories of her."
    n "还有我对她的记忆。"

# game/script.rpy:1745
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_19:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:1766
translate chinese start_8c3fde48:

    # g "Hi, Jack!"
    g "嗨，杰克！"

# game/script.rpy:1768
translate chinese start_11bb1634:

    # j "Hi."
    j "嗨。"

# game/script.rpy:1774
translate chinese start_0aef4fef:

    # g "A beautiful morning, isn't it?"
    g "多美好的早晨，是吧？"

# game/script.rpy:1780
translate chinese start_6975fc74:

    # g "Let's give it our all today!"
    g "今天让我们全力以赴工作吧！"

# game/script.rpy:1782
translate chinese start_b3158f76:

    # j "Yep. Let's do that."
    j "好。就这么办。"

# game/script.rpy:1788
translate chinese start_347a6aaf_1:

    # g "Um..."
    g "嗯……"

# game/script.rpy:1794
translate chinese start_e7d72626:

    # g "...Your uniform is kind of all... wrinkly... isn't it?"
    g "……你的工服有点……皱巴巴的……诶？"

# game/script.rpy:1796
translate chinese start_b9cdc77a:

    # j "Oh."
    j "噢。"

# game/script.rpy:1797
translate chinese start_e2827639:

    # j "Yeah, it is. I haven't got an iron, so..."
    j "对，是有点。我没有熨斗，所以……"

# game/script.rpy:1802
translate chinese start_0829bd56:

    # g "Jeez, you're really hopeless, aren't you?"
    g "老天，你真是无可救药了，对吗？"

# game/script.rpy:1804
translate chinese start_fe0f01fb:

    # j "I wouldn't go that far..."
    j "太夸张了吧……"

# game/script.rpy:1810
translate chinese start_8d99598e:

    # g "I could iron your clothes for you... if you said pretty please."
    g "我可以帮你熨衣服……只要你好好拜托我。"

# game/script.rpy:1820
translate chinese start_18f07f49:

    # n "{w=0.5}August 8"
    n "{w=0.5}8月8日"

# game/script.rpy:1821
translate chinese start_f3c11f14:

    # n "After that one time, Grace started coming up to me more and more, and talking to me more and more."
    n "从那一次之后，格瑞丝开始越来越频繁地接近我，越来越频繁地找我说话。"

# game/script.rpy:1822
translate chinese start_69bcbac4:

    # n "It was a gradual thing. Just \"Hello\" and \"Goodbye\" and \"How are you doing\" at first."
    n "这是一个循序渐进的过程。起初仅仅只有“你好”“再见”还有“你好吗”。"

# game/script.rpy:1823
translate chinese start_6007e445:

    # n "Eventually they grew to full conversations."
    n "最终这些单词短句都发展成了完整的对话。"

# game/script.rpy:1824
translate chinese start_424f28e7:

    # n "Well, I say full conversations. They were still pretty bare-bones."
    n "好吧，说是完整对话，但仍然很简单乏味。"

# game/script.rpy:1829
translate chinese start_1e77039f:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I noticed how friendly she was being, of course."
    nvl clear
    n "当然，我注意到她极尽友善。"

# game/script.rpy:1832
translate chinese start_ddd03cf3:

    # n "But I didn’t push her away."
    n "但我没有推开她。"

# game/script.rpy:1833
translate chinese start_97ff1f78:

    # n "I couldn't tell why I didn't do that."
    n "我也不知道我为什么没有。"

# game/script.rpy:1834
translate chinese start_58f84ce6:

    # n "I surprised myself every day by not telling her to screw off."
    n "每天我惊讶自己竟然没有让她滚开。"

# game/script.rpy:1836
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_20:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:1846
translate chinese start_7dc28e0a:

    # g "Hey, Jack..."
    g "嘿，杰克……"

# game/script.rpy:1850
translate chinese start_f6787422:

    # g "There's this bar just down the road. I hear it's a good place to go."
    g "这条路上有家酒吧。我听说那地方不错。"

# game/script.rpy:1857
translate chinese start_8036b9db:

    # g "So... how about we go there? After work today?"
    g "那么……我们俩一起去怎么样？今天下班后？"

# game/script.rpy:1863
translate chinese start_3d2802d6:

    # g "To relax?"
    g "去放松一下？"

# game/script.rpy:1869
translate chinese start_e820de64:

    # n "And when she asked me out for drinks, I surprised myself further by saying, \"Sure.\""
    n "她约我出去喝酒时，我说“好啊”，我对自己感到更加震惊。"

# game/script.rpy:1871
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_21:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:1901
translate chinese start_e9a43344:

    # g "How do you like it here?"
    g "你觉得这里怎么样？"

# game/script.rpy:1905
translate chinese start_d19916a3:

    # g "Is it nice?"
    g "不错吧？"

# game/script.rpy:1907
translate chinese start_ea426738:

    # j "It’s all right, I guess."
    j "挺好的，我觉得。"

# game/script.rpy:1908
translate chinese start_f56d8184:

    # j "I don’t really know, honestly. I don’t go to places like this."
    j "老实说，我不清楚。我没来过这样的地方。"

# game/script.rpy:1914
translate chinese start_5c5eb6ee:

    # g "Oh, well, I don’t either. Not a lot."
    g "噢，好吧。我也是，不怎么来。"

# game/script.rpy:1920
translate chinese start_30e83a08:

    # g "But I thought it would be fun. You know?"
    g "但我觉得会很好玩的。是吧？"

# game/script.rpy:1924
translate chinese start_67d4dd26:

    # "Grace ordered a Jack and coke."
    "格瑞丝点了一杯威士忌兑可乐。"

# game/script.rpy:1925
translate chinese start_7307d7cb:

    # "I didn’t know what to get, so I asked for one, too."
    "我不知道喝什么，所以也点了一杯一样的。"

# game/script.rpy:1944
translate chinese start_ec807b74:

    # "Our drinks came quickly."
    "我们的酒很快就上来了。"

# game/script.rpy:1945
translate chinese start_431c000b:

    # "They were cool and pleasantly sweet. But I couldn’t enjoy mine."
    "酒清凉爽口，甜度适中。但我食不甘味。"

# game/script.rpy:1946
translate chinese start_21e5c8b4:

    # "I was in a bad mood."
    "我心情很差。"

# game/script.rpy:1947
translate chinese start_e047923b:

    # "The waitress had giggled while taking my order, and I took it as an insult—or it was something else just as dumb."
    "女服务生在我点单时咯咯笑了，或者做出了其他让我感到不爽的愚蠢举动，我觉得这是一种侮辱。"

# game/script.rpy:1948
translate chinese start_3fe3476f:

    # "I can't remember exactly."
    "我记不清了。"

# game/script.rpy:1957
translate chinese start_927882db:

    # g "Ahh..."
    g "啊……"

# game/script.rpy:1961
translate chinese start_e57107fa:

    # g "Feels good to relax after a long day at work, doesn’t it?"
    g "辛苦工作一天后放松一下真惬意，对吧？"

# game/script.rpy:1963
translate chinese start_fe29fd14:

    # "I grumbled."
    "我嘟嘟囔囔。"

# game/script.rpy:1969
translate chinese start_98c4fb3a:

    # g "What is it, Jack?"
    g "你说什么，杰克？"

# game/script.rpy:1971
translate chinese start_2854dc3e:

    # j "Nothing."
    j "没什么。"

# game/script.rpy:1975
translate chinese start_64af3455:

    # "I sipped my drink."
    "我抿了一口我的酒。"

# game/script.rpy:1981
translate chinese start_26b5996c:

    # g "Um, something’s bothering you, isn’t it?"
    g "嗯，有什么烦心事吗？"

# game/script.rpy:1985
translate chinese start_cc25e2cb:

    # j "I said it’s nothing."
    j "我说了没什么。"

# game/script.rpy:1989
translate chinese start_55887b25:

    # j "I’m just not cut out for this stuff."
    j "我只是不太适应这东西。"

# game/script.rpy:1994
translate chinese start_d06520f0:

    # g "Oh, I’m sorry."
    g "噢，好可惜。"

# game/script.rpy:1999
translate chinese start_6d71243e:

    # g "You don’t have to drink if you don’t want to."
    g "你不想喝的话就不用喝了。"

# game/script.rpy:2001
translate chinese start_bd73cbfb:

    # j "I don’t mean that."
    j "我不是这个意思。"

# game/script.rpy:2002
translate chinese start_537dcf4a:

    # j "I mean all this."
    j "我是指这里的一切。"

# game/script.rpy:2004
translate chinese start_83ab0bcb:

    # "I gestured at everything around us."
    "我指了指周围的一切。"

# game/script.rpy:2006
translate chinese start_3c20371e:

    # j "Doing... things. With people."
    j "与人……接触。"

# game/script.rpy:2012
translate chinese start_9c706af3:

    # g "Huh? Why?"
    g "哈？为什么？"

# game/script.rpy:2014
translate chinese start_48d441a9:

    # j "You wouldn’t get it even if I explained. We’re just too different."
    j "我解释了你也不会明白。你和我太不同了。"

# game/script.rpy:2015
translate chinese start_08e52664:

    # j "I’ve had it rough in life."
    j "曾经我过得很艰难。"

# game/script.rpy:2021
translate chinese start_766cf03c:

    # g "Really? I’m sorry to hear that."
    g "真的吗？听你这么说我很难过。"

# game/script.rpy:2025
translate chinese start_1f1bd7ad:

    # g "But that doesn’t mean you can’t enjoy yourself now."
    g "但这并不意味着现在你不能好好享受生活。"

# game/script.rpy:2029
translate chinese start_1243629b:

    # j "I... well..."
    j "我……呃……"

# game/script.rpy:2035
translate chinese start_87cee0ad:

    # g "It would be a shame not to do fun things just because of that!"
    g "因为这个就不去做好玩的事就太可惜了！"

# game/script.rpy:2037
translate chinese start_5c97897d:

    # j "No, what I’m saying is, it’s just not fun for me."
    j "不，我的意思是，这对我来说一点也不好玩。"

# game/script.rpy:2038
translate chinese start_d93bfe1d:

    # j "I don't like this."
    j "我不喜欢。"

# game/script.rpy:2044
translate chinese start_f24ed5cf:

    # g "How can you say that? We’ve barely been here for ten minutes."
    g "你怎么知道不好玩？我们才来了十分钟。"

# game/script.rpy:2046
translate chinese start_d205d40b:

    # j "I just know."
    j "我就是知道。"

# game/script.rpy:2050
translate chinese start_46f3856b:

    # "She didn't seem happy I said that."
    "她似乎不太高兴我这么说。"

# game/script.rpy:2057
translate chinese start_dd2e560d:

    # g "So you want to leave?"
    g "那你想走了？"

# game/script.rpy:2061
translate chinese start_5a1e3d47:

    # j "Uh..."
    j "呃……"

# game/script.rpy:2063
translate chinese start_f823990f:

    # "I hadn’t actually thought of leaving. I’d just complained to complain."
    "其实我并没有想要走。我只是抱怨一下。"

# game/script.rpy:2069
translate chinese start_9c0ba3fc:

    # g "Well, you can’t leave."
    g "不行，你不能走。"

# game/script.rpy:2075
translate chinese start_1d0a02dd:

    # g "Not yet."
    g "还没到时候。"

# game/script.rpy:2077
translate chinese start_dc7d97cc:

    # j "Oh yeah?"
    j "哦是吗？"

# game/script.rpy:2084
translate chinese start_07dbf09e:

    # g "Yes!"
    g "是的！"

# game/script.rpy:2088
translate chinese start_557184dc:

    # g "If you keep going like this, you’re never gonna have any fun in life."
    g "如果你继续像这样，你就永远也发现不了生活中的乐趣。"

# game/script.rpy:2095
translate chinese start_ecbe93d9:

    # g "So promise me you’ll at least give... being with me... a chance."
    g "答应我，至少你再试一下……和我一起。"

# game/script.rpy:2097
translate chinese start_f79697f5:

    # j "You want me to stay here longer?"
    j "你想让我再呆一会？"

# game/script.rpy:2101
translate chinese start_a19a272e:

    # g "Yes."
    g "对。"

# game/script.rpy:2105
translate chinese start_0147a282:

    # g "At least another hour."
    g "至少再呆一个小时。"

# game/script.rpy:2107
translate chinese start_4a872f05:

    # j "A whole hour...?"
    j "整整一小时……？"

# game/script.rpy:2114
translate chinese start_f8e56639:

    # g "Please?"
    g "求你了？"

# game/script.rpy:2118
translate chinese start_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "……"

# game/script.rpy:2120
translate chinese start_6b2327c7:

    # j "Fine. I can do an hour."
    j "好吧。那就再一小时。"

# game/script.rpy:2127
translate chinese start_29a144e7:

    # g "Thank you!"
    g "谢谢你！"

# game/script.rpy:2133
translate chinese start_2600c7f0:

    # g "You won’t regret it."
    g "你不会后悔的。"

# game/script.rpy:2135
translate chinese start_82f24146:

    # j "Yeah. Sure."
    j "是啊，当然不会。"

# game/script.rpy:2145
translate chinese start_d1dbedc8:

    # n "It seemed like such a long time."
    n "似乎真的会很久。"

# game/script.rpy:2146
translate chinese start_a5887dae:

    # n "There was a clock on the wall opposite me."
    n "我对面的墙上挂着钟。"

# game/script.rpy:2147
translate chinese start_16697962:

    # n "I was going to stare at it for the whole hour, counting down the minutes."
    n "我打算盯着钟看整整一小时，倒数时间。"

# game/script.rpy:2149
translate chinese start_1d1b5b54:

    # nvl clear
    # n "Then, when the hour passed, I would get up and leave."
    nvl clear
    n "然后，等一小时过了，我就起身离开。"

# game/script.rpy:2152
translate chinese start_2e7a48a5:

    # n "Simple as that."
    n "就这么简单。"

# game/script.rpy:2153
translate chinese start_468259ac:

    # n "But then something happened."
    n "但后来发生了一些事。"

# game/script.rpy:2155
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_22:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:2173
translate chinese start_6db1c518:

    # n "Grace was having trouble."
    n "格瑞丝遇到了麻烦。"

# game/script.rpy:2174
translate chinese start_f1e0f359:

    # n "I had never seen her so awkward."
    n "我从未见她如此尴尬。"

# game/script.rpy:2179
translate chinese start_0a31575c:

    # n "She was stammering, struggling to find stuff to talk about."
    n "她支支吾吾，努力寻找话题。"

# game/script.rpy:2180
translate chinese start_edb00e8c:

    # n "I realized it was because I was just sitting there, barely saying anything."
    n "我意识到是因为我就呆呆坐在这，几乎一言不发。"

# game/script.rpy:2181
translate chinese start_9c7f84ea:

    # n "I was acting all grumpy, too. That couldn't have helped."
    n "我也变得焦躁。但这丝毫没有帮助。"

# game/script.rpy:2183
translate chinese start_c5bbbb66:

    # nvl clear
    # n "Back in the store, with so many distractions around us, it had been easy for her to chat with me every so often—a few words here and there."
    nvl clear
    n "在店里时，我们要应付周围那么多事，她时不时和我聊一两句就很容易。"

# game/script.rpy:2186
translate chinese start_c05b503c:

    # n "I hadn't had to do much back then besides nod."
    n "那时我除了点头之外不需要做太多的回应。"

# game/script.rpy:2187
translate chinese start_1cb05674:

    # n "Sitting down, talking face to face, it simply couldn't work like that."
    n "现在，坐下来，面对面交谈，这根本行不通。"

# game/script.rpy:2189
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_23:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:2205
translate chinese start_d2bcdc03:

    # n "After more than a few failed attempts to get the ball rolling, Grace... gave up."
    n "进行了数次尝试都以失败告终，格瑞丝……放弃了。"

# game/script.rpy:2206
translate chinese start_e0ea5368:

    # n "She sat there, looking at her drink instead of at me."
    n "她坐在那儿，不再看着我，转而盯着她的酒。"

# game/script.rpy:2208
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_24:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:2212
translate chinese start_7dd66ed2:

    # n "She was most likely working up the courage to end this early."
    n "她很可能鼓足了极大勇气，提早结束了尝试。"

# game/script.rpy:2213
translate chinese start_1e6f660a:

    # n "In just a few minutes, I'd be free to leave."
    n "再有几分钟后，我就自由了。"

# game/script.rpy:2215
translate chinese start_83c133f9:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I found I couldn't stand that."
    nvl clear
    n "但我发现我受不了这气氛了。"

# game/script.rpy:2222
translate chinese start_e9d9b105:

    # n "So I started talking."
    n "于是我开始说话。"

# game/script.rpy:2223
translate chinese start_e47a74f9:

    # n "I said the first thing that came to mind, no matter how stupid."
    n "我说出了脑子里第一个想到的东西，不管有多傻。"

# game/script.rpy:2225
translate chinese start_3efd9a7a:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I don't know why I did it."
    nvl clear
    n "我不知道我为什么要这样做。"

# game/script.rpy:2228
translate chinese start_9ad4e361:

    # n "It feels so unlike me—both feeling bad for someone and talking with no filter."
    n "感觉这很不像我——为别人感到难受，又口无遮拦地说话。"

# game/script.rpy:2229
translate chinese start_f1e8841a:

    # n "Or unlike the past me."
    n "或者说不像过去的我。"

# game/script.rpy:2231
translate chinese start_6bd8dd4b:

    # nvl clear
    # n "Maybe I was finally warming up to Grace. Or maybe it was the alcohol."
    nvl clear
    n "也许我终于和格瑞丝熟络起来了。也许是酒精在作祟。"

# game/script.rpy:2234
translate chinese start_bf74647e:

    # n "I don't know. Maybe it was both."
    n "我不知道。也许两者皆有。"

# game/script.rpy:2235
translate chinese start_b80f7811:

    # n "The reason doesn't matter. What matters is that it happened."
    n "原因不重要了。重要的是我的的确确这样做了。"

# game/script.rpy:2237
translate chinese start_a6abbc41:

    # nvl clear
    # n "Back then, there was a part of me that never relaxed, no matter what."
    nvl clear
    n "在那时，无论如何，我的有一部分从未放松下来过。"

# game/script.rpy:2240
translate chinese start_4fe8b6c7:

    # n "No, it wasn't even a part of me. Pretty much all of me was like that."
    n "不，不仅仅是我的一部分。几乎我整个人都是这样。"

# game/script.rpy:2241
translate chinese start_4a704d23:

    # n "Like a fist that wouldn’t unclench."
    n "像一个从未松开的拳头。"

# game/script.rpy:2243
translate chinese start_a0885e19:

    # nvl clear
    # n "But now I found I could relax it, little by little by little..."
    nvl clear
    n "但是现在我发现我可以放松了，一点一点地……"

# game/script.rpy:2252
translate chinese start_7a708e4d:

    # n "...and before I knew it, I really was having fun in this girl's presence—talking to her, laughing with her, simply spending time with her."
    n "……不知不觉中，我真的在和这个女孩的相处中找到了乐趣——我们一起聊天，一起大笑，一起度过美好时光。"

# game/script.rpy:2254
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_25:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:2259
translate chinese start_cbb8d540:

    # n "What did we talk about?"
    n "我们都聊些什么呢？"

# game/script.rpy:2260
translate chinese start_32578c24:

    # n "I don’t remember."
    n "我不记得了。"

# game/script.rpy:2261
translate chinese start_f302b973:

    # n "What I do remembers is that I had more fun than I'd had in years."
    n "我只记得我获得了多年来从未有过的快乐。"

# game/script.rpy:2262
translate chinese start_b77a6773:

    # n "When the hour passed, I didn't say anything. We stayed there for hours longer."
    n "一小时过去了，我也没有提起。我们还在那里多呆了几小时。"

# game/script.rpy:2264
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_26:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:2272
translate chinese start_37748de8:

    # "I do remember one thing we talked about, actually."
    "实际上，我真真切切记得我们谈过的一件事。"

# game/script.rpy:2284
translate chinese start_b1c820b2:

    # "We somehow got on the topic of family."
    "不知怎的，我们聊到了家庭。"

# game/script.rpy:2288
translate chinese start_8dd9fe4d:

    # g "What is your family like, Jack?"
    g "杰克，你的家庭是怎样的？"

# game/script.rpy:2290
translate chinese start_bed38e02:

    # j "Ah, I... I can't say."
    j "啊，我……我不能说。"

# game/script.rpy:2297
translate chinese start_e71f9894:

    # g "Oh. I see."
    g "噢。我理解。"

# game/script.rpy:2303
translate chinese start_b9f158fb:

    # g "You don't have to talk about it if you don't want to."
    g "你不想说的话就别说了。"

# game/script.rpy:2309
translate chinese start_1b94d26c:

    # g "I'm sorry I asked."
    g "对不起，我问了这个问题。"

# game/script.rpy:2314
translate chinese start_28fb7b3c:

    # g "I'm kind of... not on speaking terms with my family, either."
    g "我也……和我的家人关系不太好。"

# game/script.rpy:2316
translate chinese start_e44ec86e:

    # j "Why is that?"
    j "怎么了？"

# game/script.rpy:2322
translate chinese start_551d2b36:

    # g "That's, um..."
    g "就是，呃……"

# game/script.rpy:2328
translate chinese start_00a312de:

    # g "Actually, I don't really talk with other people all that much. Or hang out with them."
    g "其实，我不怎么会和其他人说这么多话，也不会和其他人一起出去玩。"

# game/script.rpy:2333
translate chinese start_6d551c27:

    # g "Well, outside of work."
    g "嗯，工作之余的时候。"

# game/script.rpy:2339
translate chinese start_413e7685:

    # g "I'm kind of... alone a lot of the time."
    g "我算是……很多时候都一个人。"

# game/script.rpy:2341
translate chinese start_25afcc0b:

    # j "What? Really?"
    j "什么？真的？"

# game/script.rpy:2347
translate chinese start_b4787291:

    # g "Yeah. Haha."
    g "是啊。哈哈。"

# game/script.rpy:2349
translate chinese start_496460c8:

    # "This surprised me."
    "这让我很惊讶。"

# game/script.rpy:2350
translate chinese start_5b50b96c:

    # "I was surprised a lot back then."
    "我当时大吃一惊。"

# game/script.rpy:2351
translate chinese start_073ca20b:

    # "I never thought Grace was anything like me."
    "我从未想过格瑞丝和我是同类。"

# game/script.rpy:2353
translate chinese start_5cb97123:

    # j "But you're so friendly with the people at the store."
    j "但在店里你对别人都很友好。"

# game/script.rpy:2359
translate chinese start_be26ba27:

    # g "That's all it is."
    g "仅此而已。"

# game/script.rpy:2366
translate chinese start_3772f204:

    # g "It's not that I wouldn't like to spend more time with them, but..."
    g "并不是我不想更多地和他们接触，只是……"

# game/script.rpy:2371
translate chinese start_58cac369:

    # g "I don't know. It feels like if I let them in, they're going to turn out... not nice."
    g "我不知道。感觉好像如果我接纳了他们，他们就会露出不好的那一面。"

# game/script.rpy:2377
translate chinese start_29e8caf7:

    # g "But you're different."
    g "但你不一样。"

# game/script.rpy:2382
translate chinese start_f6c8ca42:

    # g "You're just trying to get by. I don't think you'd... use someone."
    g "你只是在尽力过自己的生活。我觉得你不会……利用别人。"

# game/script.rpy:2388
translate chinese start_6f48b2f3:

    # g "God, when I say it like that, it doesn't sound right at all."
    g "天啊，我这样说，听起来一点也不对劲。"

# game/script.rpy:2393
translate chinese start_37b70dcd:

    # g "You must think I'm really weird."
    g "你一定觉得我很古怪。"

# game/script.rpy:2398
translate chinese start_d921925a:

    # g "I'm sorry."
    g "对不起。"

# game/script.rpy:2400
translate chinese start_d512a353:

    # j "No... I don't think you are."
    j "不……我不觉得你古怪。"

# game/script.rpy:2401
translate chinese start_d8ac42b5:

    # j "It makes sense, what you said."
    j "你说的，我都理解。"

# game/script.rpy:2407
translate chinese start_6f0203a1:

    # g "Really?"
    g "真的吗？"

# game/script.rpy:2413
translate chinese start_a9462233:

    # g "...Thank you, Jack."
    g "……谢谢你，杰克。"

# game/script.rpy:2419
translate chinese start_f488469c:

    # g "I really, really hoped you'd understand. And I'm so happy that you do."
    g "我真的真的希望你能理解。我也很高兴你可以理解。"

# game/script.rpy:2424
translate chinese start_df6cf0c9:

    # g "I really feel like you're... someone I can trust."
    g "我发自内心觉得我……可以信任你。"

# game/script.rpy:2434
translate chinese start_e9a03628:

    # n "We went for drinks again next week, and then once more the week after."
    n "下周我们又去喝酒了，再下周也去了。"

# game/script.rpy:2446
translate chinese start_63b8498a:

    # n "The week after that, we had dinner together, at a greasy little restaurant where we could afford to eat."
    n "后来的一周，我们在一家便宜的油腻小餐馆，一起共进晚餐。"

# game/script.rpy:2448
translate chinese start_d3807c74:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I tried to impress her by ordering wine."
    nvl clear
    n "我点了红酒，想让她开心。"

# game/script.rpy:2451
translate chinese start_c9601441:

    # n "I’d never had wine."
    n "我从来没喝过红酒。"

# game/script.rpy:2455
translate chinese start_a79579b5:

    # n "It was disgusting. But I had guessed it would be disgusting, so I forced my way through a glass anyway."
    n "味道很恶心。但我以为红酒就是这种恶心的味道，所以我还是强迫自己喝了一杯。"

# game/script.rpy:2456
translate chinese start_7ecc511f:

    # n "I even said it was delicious."
    n "我还说很好喝。"

# game/script.rpy:2458
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_27:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:2462
translate chinese start_43ef5a6b:

    # n "Then Grace tried some, told me it was spoiled."
    n "格瑞丝也尝了一点，她告诉我这酒变质了。"

# game/script.rpy:2466
translate chinese start_422fa1a4:

    # n "She teased the hell out of me for that."
    n "为此她狠狠取笑了我一番。"

# game/script.rpy:2467
translate chinese start_3828b353:

    # n "I wasn’t bitter about it. I laughed along."
    n "我并没有感到难受。我跟着一起笑了。"

# game/script.rpy:2468
translate chinese start_07456756:

    # n "Strange how quickly people can change, sometimes."
    n "真奇妙啊，有时人可以变得这么快。"

# game/script.rpy:2474
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_28:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:2478
translate chinese start_aa91a317:

    # n "Soon we started going out more often—to bars, cheap restaurants, places like that."
    n "很快我们一起出去的次数变得更加频繁——一起去酒吧、便宜餐馆之类的地方。"

# game/script.rpy:2482
translate chinese start_c085a8bc:

    # n "We took a lot of walks together, too. And one time we even went to the movies."
    n "我们也经常一起散步。有一次我们甚至一起看了电影。"

# game/script.rpy:2484
translate chinese start_7f473818:

    # nvl clear
    # n "After about a month of this, I asked Grace if she’d be my girlfriend."
    nvl clear
    n "大概一个月之后，我问格瑞丝愿不愿意做我女朋友。"

# game/script.rpy:2490
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_29:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:2501
translate chinese start_fcf5aea9:

    # g "What, am I not your girlfriend already?"
    g "啊？我不已经是你女朋友了吗？"

# game/script.rpy:2503
translate chinese start_b9cdc77a_1:

    # j "Oh."
    j "噢。"

# game/script.rpy:2505
translate chinese start_99c956bd:

    # "And that’s how it went."
    "事情经过就是这样。"

# game/script.rpy:2517
translate chinese start_72f3f27a:

    # n "August 9"
    n "8月9日"

# game/script.rpy:2518
translate chinese start_7711663c:

    # n "A few weeks later, she told me what had happened to her back when she still lived with her family."
    n "几周后，她告诉了我她之前还和家人同住时发生的一些事。"

# game/script.rpy:2519
translate chinese start_b8d80be5:

    # n "I’d known for a while that {i}something{/i} had happened—something she hadn't shared with anyone before—but when she told me what it was..."
    n "我早就察觉到肯定发生了{i}什么{/i} ，她从未将这些事告诉其他人，但她向我坦白了……"

# game/script.rpy:2520
translate chinese start_bab76686:

    # n "A few of the things she said..."
    n "她告诉我的一些事……"

# game/script.rpy:2522
translate chinese start_bffb3875:

    # nvl clear
    # n "No, I shouldn’t write it down here."
    nvl clear
    n "不，我不该在这写下来。"

# game/script.rpy:2525
translate chinese start_04fcfc81:

    # n "It feels wrong."
    n "这不对劲。"

# game/script.rpy:2526
translate chinese start_b0593587:

    # n "It’s not mine to tell."
    n "这不是我该说的。"

# game/script.rpy:2527
translate chinese start_06ef9ba8:

    # n "What if someone found this journal?"
    n "万一有人发现这本日记了呢？"

# game/script.rpy:2529
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_30:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:2537
translate chinese start_27002048:

    # "I had never imagined she was living with such a burden."
    "我从未想到她背负着这样的重担。"

# game/script.rpy:2538
translate chinese start_763eb446:

    # "When I found out, I felt crushed."
    "我知道后，我感到天旋地转。"

# game/script.rpy:2547
translate chinese start_85ce65c6:

    # j "That’s..."
    j "这也太……"

# game/script.rpy:2551
translate chinese start_5f6f2264:

    # g "I know."
    g "我知道。"

# game/script.rpy:2557
translate chinese start_c2280a97:

    # j "God, I feel like an {i}idiot.{/i}"
    j "天，我觉得自己就是个{i}白痴{/i}。"

# game/script.rpy:2558
translate chinese start_862be29e:

    # j "And after I told you I’d had it rough..."
    j "我还和你倒苦水，说我过得有多艰难……"

# game/script.rpy:2564
translate chinese start_87663c5c:

    # g "No, it’s fine."
    g "不，没事的啦。"

# game/script.rpy:2568
translate chinese start_d5d5651d:

    # g "Don’t feel bad about it, please."
    g "不用为此感到难过，好吗？"

# game/script.rpy:2572
translate chinese start_36ce13b1:

    # g "You’ve got your troubles, and I’ve got mine."
    g "我们各有各的难处。"

# game/script.rpy:2574
translate chinese start_94739297:

    # j "I know, but..."
    j "我知道，但……"

# game/script.rpy:2578
translate chinese start_1c38595d:

    # j "Can’t we {i}do{/i} something?"
    j "我们还能{i}做{/i}点什么吧？"

# game/script.rpy:2585
translate chinese start_923697b2:

    # g "There’s nothing to do. It’s all over now."
    g "无事可做，无能为力。一切都结束了。"

# game/script.rpy:2592
translate chinese start_58c874e5:

    # g "All I can do is keep looking forward."
    g "我能做的只有继续向前看。"

# game/script.rpy:2596
translate chinese start_be007616:

    # g "You know?"
    g "对吗？"

# game/script.rpy:2604
translate chinese start_64b5f177:

    # n "I hugged her and told her how brave she was for telling me."
    n "我抱住她，告诉她，她能说出来真的好勇敢。"

# game/script.rpy:2605
translate chinese start_ffe31e09:

    # n "I told her I’d protect her, keep her safe forever. And I meant it."
    n "我告诉她我会保护她，永远护她周全。我是认真的。"

# game/script.rpy:2606
translate chinese start_c1160ae3:

    # n "And I failed her—but that comes later."
    n "但我辜负了她——这是后话了。"

# game/script.rpy:2607
translate chinese start_76d90e60:

    # n "For now, I figured I should tell her what my own troubles had been."
    n "现在，我想我也该向她坦白我自己的问题。"

# game/script.rpy:2609
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_31:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:2622
translate chinese start_7f3d26d4:

    # g "Um, you don’t have to tell me if you don’t want to."
    g "嗯，如果你不想说的话就算了。"

# game/script.rpy:2626
translate chinese start_ba18b5a5:

    # j "It’s okay."
    j "没关系的。"

# game/script.rpy:2627
translate chinese start_bde087c0:

    # j "I do want to."
    j "我想告诉你的。"

# game/script.rpy:2633
translate chinese start_f8d73e61:

    # n "I’d managed to keep quiet about my past. I had only alluded to things."
    n "曾经我想方设法对自己的过去缄口不言。我只提及了只言片语。"

# game/script.rpy:2634
translate chinese start_d4cb9627:

    # n "Now I told her everything."
    n "现在我把一切都告诉她了。"

# game/script.rpy:2636
translate chinese start_a99cb930:

    # nvl clear
    # n "It wasn’t a long story."
    nvl clear
    n "这并不是一个冗长的故事。"

# game/script.rpy:2640
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_32:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:2650
translate chinese start_491f2dfd:

    # g "What? Nothing?"
    g "什么？什么都不记得了？"

# game/script.rpy:2656
translate chinese start_5ff77c33:

    # g "You don’t remember anything?"
    g "你忘记了所有事情？"

# game/script.rpy:2658
translate chinese start_f8b04926:

    # j "Okay, it’s not exactly {i}nothing{/i}."
    j "呃，准确来说并不是{i}什么都不记得{/i}。"

# game/script.rpy:2659
translate chinese start_1ae08117:

    # j "But my teen years are fuzzy. And everything before that, it’s like it doesn’t exist."
    j "我十几岁时的记忆模模糊糊的。而在此之前的一切，就好像不存在一样。"

# game/script.rpy:2664
translate chinese start_a2b77d17:

    # g "What about your family?"
    g "那你的家人呢？"

# game/script.rpy:2666
translate chinese start_beb605d3:

    # j "I don’t know. Maybe I had one."
    j "我不知道。我好像有一个家人吧。"

# game/script.rpy:2667
translate chinese start_02100923:

    # j "I was in a lot of institutions before I turned eighteen."
    j "我十八岁之前呆过好几家福利院。"

# game/script.rpy:2673
translate chinese start_4a306f1d:

    # g "Oh, Jack..."
    g "噢，杰克……"

# game/script.rpy:2675
translate chinese start_eb95d01a:

    # j "I’ll tell you about those times if you want. But there’s not a lot to tell."
    j "如果你想听的话，我可以告诉你那时的事。但也没什么可说的。"

# game/script.rpy:2676
translate chinese start_dce87c54:

    # j "Nothing really ever happened to me."
    j "其实我身上真的没有发生什么事。"

# game/script.rpy:2677
translate chinese start_a99fa9bb:

    # j "I wish I could tell you everything about my life. I really do. But I can’t."
    j "我也想把我的一切都告诉你。我是真心的。但我不记得了。"

# game/script.rpy:2682
translate chinese start_7e8d1ae5:

    # g "That’s fine..."
    g "没事的……"

# game/script.rpy:2689
translate chinese start_a20cefa7_1:

    # "..."
    "……"

# game/script.rpy:2696
translate chinese start_331422f0:

    # g "Did you ever try to find out?"
    g "那你试过找回记忆吗？"

# game/script.rpy:2698
translate chinese start_31aed483:

    # j "About my life before then?"
    j "找回我过去的记忆吗？"

# game/script.rpy:2702
translate chinese start_eebba2e7:

    # g "Yeah."
    g "对。"

# game/script.rpy:2720
translate chinese start_ad512e24:

    # j "I didn’t."
    j "没有。"

# game/script.rpy:2726
translate chinese start_658a2806:

    # g "Why not?"
    g "为什么不试试呢？"

# game/script.rpy:2730
translate chinese start_2c40019e:

    # j "Uh, I don’t know."
    j "呃，我不知道。"

# game/script.rpy:2731
translate chinese start_9fa287c1:

    # j "I just never felt like it, I guess."
    j "我想我就是没什么感觉。"

# game/script.rpy:2733
translate chinese start_b166a66d:

    # "I must’ve known, even back then, that some memories are best left buried."
    "就算在过去，我一定也明白，有些记忆还是忘却了最好。"

# game/script.rpy:2740
translate chinese start_9a156a3a:

    # g "I’m sure I would like to remember, if I couldn’t."
    g "如果忘不掉的话，我肯定还会想起来的。"

# game/script.rpy:2747
translate chinese start_2e7a21e9:

    # g "But you’re fine with it?"
    g "不过你真的没事吗？"

# game/script.rpy:2749
translate chinese start_fcceffc0:

    # j "Yeah."
    j "没事的。"

# game/script.rpy:2756
translate chinese start_011e3580:

    # g "Well, okay."
    g "嗯，好吧。"

# game/script.rpy:2762
translate chinese start_bd53fa7a:

    # g "Tell me about the times you can remember, then."
    g "那么把你还记得的都告诉我吧。"

# game/script.rpy:2766
translate chinese start_161cbe90:

    # "So I went on to tell her all about the few bland memories I had."
    "于是我接着和她讲了我所记得的几段平淡往事。"

# game/script.rpy:2784
translate chinese start_ee1f6bbc:

    # n "August 10"
    n "8月10日"

# game/script.rpy:2785
translate chinese start_f1d0c69c:

    # n "I could write about all the talks we had, about the first night we spent together, about looking for an apartment and then finding it, about moving in..."
    n "我能写下我们所有的谈话，写下我们一起度过的第一个夜晚，写下我们一起租到公寓，写下我们的同居生活……"

# game/script.rpy:2786
translate chinese start_688b5303:

    # n "About pretty much anything that only involved the two of us. But I think it’s time to move on."
    n "我能写下所有专属于我们两人的秘密。但我想是时候翻篇了。"

# game/script.rpy:2787
translate chinese start_92ec6f08:

    # n "This isn’t a feel-good journal, after all."
    n "毕竟，这本日记不是拿来记录甜蜜往事的。"

# game/script.rpy:2791
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_33:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:2801
translate chinese start_86e20fb3:

    # n "It was a Thursday, coming up to a year since Grace and I started dating."
    n "今天是周三，距离我和格瑞丝开始约会已经一年了。"

# game/script.rpy:2802
translate chinese start_c4f86d57:

    # n "I was at the cash register. Grace wasn’t in the store."
    n "我站在收银台。格瑞丝不在店里。"

# game/script.rpy:2803
translate chinese start_b5da185d:

    # n "An old lady was counting her change—slowly and with trembling hands—when Anna walked in."
    n "一个老太太在数她的零钱，她动作迟缓双手微抖。这时安娜进来了。"

# game/script.rpy:2805
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_34:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:2809
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_35:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:2831
translate chinese start_af02a49b:

    # "Anna didn’t buy anything."
    "安娜什么也没买。"

# game/script.rpy:2836
translate chinese start_5d60194e:

    # "She went for the register—towards me—empty-handed."
    "她走向收银台，目标锁定我，两手空空。"

# game/script.rpy:2837
translate chinese start_0e22f57b:

    # "The sight of her approaching made my heart start beating like mad. My head hurt."
    "看到她走过来，我的心开始疯了一样砰砰狂跳。我的头隐隐作痛。"

# game/script.rpy:2838
translate chinese start_580fcb34:

    # "I knew the moment I saw her that she meant trouble."
    "我看到她的第一眼就知道她来者不善。"

# game/script.rpy:2844
translate chinese start_e8d0305a:

    # a "Jack?"
    a "杰克？"

# game/script.rpy:2848
translate chinese start_59540605:

    # a "My God, is that you, Jack?"
    a "我的天呀，杰克，是你吗？"

# game/script.rpy:2852
translate chinese start_31d38ea7:

    # "She had the nerve to pretend she’d stumbled upon me by accident. Like she hadn’t tracked me down."
    "她还好意思装作是偶然碰到我的。好像她没有跟踪我一样。"

# game/script.rpy:2853
translate chinese start_018ede19:

    # "But I didn’t have it together. I couldn’t see through her acting."
    "但那时我无法保持冷静。我没有识破她的装模做样。"

# game/script.rpy:2854
translate chinese start_eb9a13a7:

    # "I was confused—panicking, not sure why."
    "我又困惑又恐慌，不知道为什么。"

# game/script.rpy:2856
translate chinese start_5219c6b7:

    # j "Excuse me, miss?"
    j "不好意思，女士？"

# game/script.rpy:2862
translate chinese start_837ba923:

    # a "Is it you?"
    a "是你吗？"

# game/script.rpy:2866
translate chinese start_b4fa3fc0:

    # j "..."
    j "……"

# game/script.rpy:2867
translate chinese start_6e4b2b6c:

    # j "Please don’t cut in line, miss. It’s not fair to the other customers."
    j "女士，请不要插队。这样对其他顾客不公平。"

# game/script.rpy:2873
translate chinese start_9137fe84:

    # "The old lady was still tackling her mass of coins. She didn’t seem to notice much around her."
    "那个老太太还在清点她那一大堆硬币。她似乎没注意到周围发生了什么。"

# game/script.rpy:2880
translate chinese start_c8ff6726:

    # a "Don’t play silly with me, Jack. It’s you, isn’t it?"
    a "别逗我了，杰克。你真的是杰克对吧？"

# game/script.rpy:2882
translate chinese start_ecd9d53d:

    # j "Yes, my name is Jack. But you’ve got me confused with someone else."
    j "是的，我是叫杰克。但你应该是认错人了。"

# game/script.rpy:2883
translate chinese start_70a82ed7:

    # j "There’s a lot of Jacks out there."
    j "和我同名的人很多。"

# game/script.rpy:2887
translate chinese start_8c4c9eaa:

    # a "Oh, come on. You’re you, all right."
    a "噢，别闹了。就是你，好吗。"

# game/script.rpy:2889
translate chinese start_731c5bfe:

    # "I put a hand on the counter, to steady myself."
    "我伸出一只手杵在柜台上，好稳住我自己。"

# game/script.rpy:2896
translate chinese start_7cd97077:

    # "She reached out as if to place her hands on mine."
    "她也伸出手，好像要叠在我的手上。"

# game/script.rpy:2902
translate chinese start_1ae666fb:

    # "I jerked my hand back like she was going to bite me."
    "我猛地把手缩回，仿佛她要吃了我一样。"

# game/script.rpy:2908
translate chinese start_9e886a5e:

    # a "It’s me. It’s Anna."
    a "是我呀，我是安娜。"

# game/script.rpy:2912
translate chinese start_44afdb65:

    # a "Don’t you remember your... old friend?"
    a "你不记得你的……老朋友了吗？"

# game/script.rpy:2914
translate chinese start_91143186:

    # j "No. We’ve never met."
    j "不，我们从来没见过。"

# game/script.rpy:2920
translate chinese start_cfc17b6c:

    # a "...I guess it {i}has{/i} been a while. Fifteen years?"
    a "……我记得{i}已经{/i} 过去好多年了。十五年了对吗？"

# game/script.rpy:2922
translate chinese start_b930f4b2:

    # j "Not me. Must be someone else."
    j "不是我。你认错人了。"

# game/script.rpy:2929
translate chinese start_6c03e1b8:

    # "Anna stared right at me. {i}Through{/i} me."
    "安娜直勾勾地盯着我。锐利的目光快把我{i}刺透{/i} 。"

# game/script.rpy:2930
translate chinese start_9a3563ec:

    # "I thought I’d either boil or freeze."
    "我的感官忽上忽下，一下如热锅上的蚂蚁焦躁不安，一下又感到天寒地冻的刺骨冰冷。"

# game/script.rpy:2936
translate chinese start_94780989:

    # a "Sure it’s you."
    a "得了吧，就是你。"

# game/script.rpy:2940
translate chinese start_81a41aa3:

    # a "Let’s go somewhere and talk about old times. I know a great restaurant just two streets over."
    a "我们找个地方叙叙旧吧。我知道两条街外有家不错的餐厅。"

# game/script.rpy:2944
translate chinese start_51f7f2a1:

    # j "Look, lady."
    j "行了，女士。"

# game/script.rpy:2948
translate chinese start_1d5a3680:

    # j "Even if I was this friend of yours, I have a job to do."
    j "就算我是你朋友，我现在也得工作。"

# game/script.rpy:2949
translate chinese start_834d6902:

    # j "So let me get on with it. You’re bothering the customers."
    j "能让我继续工作吗？你妨碍到其他顾客了。"

# game/script.rpy:2951
translate chinese start_c6e02a5d:

    # "The customers weren’t bothered one bit."
    "虽然顾客好像一点也没受到影响。"

# game/script.rpy:2952
translate chinese start_7f773a39:

    # "If they hated anyone, it was probably me. After all, I was being so rude to this pretty, charming girl who only wanted to talk to her friend."
    "如果他们要厌恶谁的话，应该只会厌恶我。毕竟，这个漂亮迷人的女孩只是想和我说说话，我的态度却如此粗鲁恶劣。"

# game/script.rpy:2956
translate chinese start_00431880:

    # a "That’s a good point, Jack."
    a "这个理由还说得过去，杰克。"

# game/script.rpy:2960
translate chinese start_053f7279:

    # a "What are you doing in this place? It’s a pile of trash."
    a "你在这种地方做什么？这看起来就是个垃圾场。"

# game/script.rpy:2966
translate chinese start_5dc45292:

    # a "Someone like {i}you{/i} doesn’t belong here."
    a "{i}你{/i}这样的人不属于这里。"

# game/script.rpy:2968
translate chinese start_e34ecac4:

    # "I was through trying to reason with her."
    "我不想再和她多费口舌。"

# game/script.rpy:2969
translate chinese start_64eb8429:

    # "I crossed my arms and said nothing, hoping she wouldn’t notice that my heart was pounding way too fast."
    "我抱起双臂，什么也没说，我希望她不要注意到我心跳过速。"

# game/script.rpy:2973
translate chinese start_2e72bc67:

    # "Anna gave me a good, hard look."
    "安娜狠狠地看了我一眼。"

# game/script.rpy:2975
translate chinese start_a20cefa7_2:

    # "..."
    "……"

# game/script.rpy:2982
translate chinese start_dc7e6b37:

    # a "So that's how it is."
    a "那就这样吧。"

# game/script.rpy:2986
translate chinese start_c94d0cd1:

    # a "I’ll see you later, Jack."
    a "回见，杰克。"

# game/script.rpy:2992
translate chinese start_b327d886:

    # "And she went away."
    "她走了。"

# game/script.rpy:2993
translate chinese start_80950ebf:

    # "I let out a long breath I hadn’t noticed I was holding."
    "我都没有注意到我屏住了呼吸，我长长吁了一口气。"

# game/script.rpy:2994
translate chinese start_5b256078:

    # "I felt awful."
    "我感觉糟透了。"

# game/script.rpy:2995
translate chinese start_e91db3db:

    # "Even worse, I felt Anna had been right. There had definitely been something familiar about her."
    "更糟的是，我感觉安娜是对的。她身上有种东西似曾相识。"

# game/script.rpy:2996
translate chinese start_d14f8dbd:

    # "But I didn’t want to find out more."
    "但我不想深入了解。"

# game/script.rpy:2997
translate chinese start_05e3a01d:

    # "{i}Next time she comes in, I’ll treat her the same way,{/i} I told myself, guessing correctly there’d be a next time, guessing wrongly that it’d be at the store."
    "{i}下一次她来，我还是会用同样的方式对待她，{/i}我告诉自己，猜对了还会有下一次，猜错了我们就止于这家店吧。"

# game/script.rpy:2998
translate chinese start_5302cfac:

    # "{i}I’ll do it again and again, until she gives up. I don’t know what she wants, but I won’t give an inch.{/i}"
    "{i}我会反复这样做，直到她知难而退。我不知道她想要什么，但我不会让步的。{/i}"

# game/script.rpy:2999
translate chinese start_b2fa72d6:

    # "{w=0.25}.{w=0.5}.{w=0.5}."
    "{w=0.25}.{w=0.5}.{w=0.5}."

# game/script.rpy:3000
translate chinese start_c7e9547f:

    # "The old lady cried out. She’d found a quarter."
    "老太太大叫一声。她找到了一枚两角五分的硬币。"

# game/script.rpy:3010
translate chinese start_a7aa0587:

    # n "August 11"
    n "8月11日"

# game/script.rpy:3011
translate chinese start_53e7810b:

    # n "It’s weird, isn’t it? How I just write today’s date like that and then go right to telling about something that happened months ago?"
    n "很奇怪，对吧？我怎么就这样写着今天的日期，然后讲述着几个月前发生的事？"

# game/script.rpy:3012
translate chinese start_a2b848a0:

    # n "I should write down when that stuff happened."
    n "我应该写下事情发生时的日期。"

# game/script.rpy:3013
translate chinese start_5b89a28c:

    # n "But it was so long ago. I don’t think I can remember the exact dates."
    n "但那是好久之前的事了。我想我不记得确切是哪天发生的了。"

# game/script.rpy:3015
translate chinese start_422873a4:

    # nvl clear
    # n "Ah, who cares."
    nvl clear
    n "啊，管他呢。"

# game/script.rpy:3018
translate chinese start_1cea96ae:

    # n "This is only for me, anyway. It can be a jumbled mess."
    n "反正也只有我一个人会看。这就是一团乱麻。"

# game/script.rpy:3020
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_36:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3024
translate chinese start_5aff393a:

    # n "Sometimes I feel like I should write more about what’s happening {i}now.{/i}"
    n "有时我觉得我应该多写一些{i}当下{/i}发生的事。"

# game/script.rpy:3025
translate chinese start_33ddcc99:

    # n "But nothing is happening."
    n "但当下无事发生。"

# game/script.rpy:3026
translate chinese start_c14c0a9a:

    # n "So fuck it."
    n "去他的。"

# game/script.rpy:3028
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_37:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3034
translate chinese start_ef8dafee:

    # n "When I told Grace about the girl who called herself Anna—and who called me Jack even though we didn’t wear name tags—she took it like it was good news."
    n "我跟格瑞丝讲了那个自称安娜的女孩，我都没戴名牌，她却知道我叫杰克。格瑞丝觉得这是件好事。"

# game/script.rpy:3036
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_38:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3051
translate chinese start_b9d4592b:

    # g "That’s amazing, Jack!"
    g "好神奇，杰克！"

# game/script.rpy:3057
translate chinese start_4558e925:

    # g "She must’ve recognized you from childhood. She said fifteen years, didn’t she?"
    g "她一定从你小时候就认识你了。她不是说已经十五年了吗？"

# game/script.rpy:3061
translate chinese start_a7d7a4b0:

    # g "That’s right from the time you can’t remember."
    g "正好是你失去记忆的那段时间。"

# game/script.rpy:3063
translate chinese start_b69435c3:

    # j "I don’t know. She might be some sort of scam artist."
    j "不知道。她可能是什么骗子。"

# game/script.rpy:3065
translate chinese start_ab413df3:

    # "I’d just come up with that idea—of Anna being a scam artist."
    "我说出了我的想法——安娜是个骗子。"

# game/script.rpy:3066
translate chinese start_1a708e7c:

    # "It seemed a good enough excuse not to go near her again."
    "看上去是个能不再接近她的好借口。"

# game/script.rpy:3072
translate chinese start_b479e59a:

    # g "Yeah, right."
    g "啊，就是这样。"

# game/script.rpy:3078
translate chinese start_d2cfed94:

    # g "Come on, Jack—at least give her the benefit of the doubt."
    g "别这样，杰克，至少相信她没有恶意吧？"

# game/script.rpy:3080
translate chinese start_63ab84c5:

    # j "I don’t need her, Grace."
    j "我没必要和她认识，格瑞丝。"

# game/script.rpy:3081
translate chinese start_eafa78eb:

    # j "I’ve got you."
    j "我已经有你了。"

# game/script.rpy:3087
translate chinese start_57d83d45:

    # g "Jack, I’m not telling you to sleep with her."
    g "杰克，我又不是要让你和她干什么。"

# game/script.rpy:3093
translate chinese start_3a1baf82:

    # g "Don’t be so rude to her next time, okay?"
    g "下次别那么粗暴地对她，好吗？"

# game/script.rpy:3097
translate chinese start_522af360:

    # j "I wasn’t being rude."
    j "我没有粗暴。"

# game/script.rpy:3104
translate chinese start_8efcb18f:

    # g "You so were."
    g "你有。"

# game/script.rpy:3106
translate chinese start_c9221505:

    # j "Okay, so what if I was?"
    j "行行行，那又怎样呢？"

# game/script.rpy:3113
translate chinese start_b3d23959:

    # g "It’s not fair to her."
    g "这对她不公平。"

# game/script.rpy:3117
translate chinese start_023c520b:

    # g "She seems like a nice girl."
    g "她看上去是个好女孩。"

# game/script.rpy:3121
translate chinese start_64061eea:

    # g "And don’t you think it’d be good for you, too?"
    g "这样对你自己也好，不是吗？"

# game/script.rpy:3123
translate chinese start_f228322b:

    # j "To be friends with her? No, not really."
    j "和她交朋友？不，别了吧。"

# game/script.rpy:3127
translate chinese start_763408f0:

    # g "She could tell you about your past."
    g "她能告诉你你的过去。"

# game/script.rpy:3131
translate chinese start_695fae58:

    # g "Then maybe some things would start making sense. You could put whatever happened behind you."
    g "有些事应该就可以说得通了。无论发生什么，你都可以释怀了。"

# game/script.rpy:3135
translate chinese start_49d5c360:

    # j "But nothing happened."
    j "但真的没有发生什么。"

# game/script.rpy:3140
translate chinese start_df390230:

    # g "...{i}Something{/i} must have happened, Jack."
    g "……一定{i}有事{/i} 发生，杰克。"

# game/script.rpy:3146
translate chinese start_83dda368:

    # g "People don’t..."
    g "否则一般人不会……"

# game/script.rpy:3152
translate chinese start_89b820dd:

    # "Grace fell silent. Instead of continuing, she started running her fork through the peas on her plate."
    "格瑞丝沉默了。她开始用叉子戳着盘子里的豌豆，没再说话。"

# game/script.rpy:3153
translate chinese start_18cc43b4:

    # "We were having dinner."
    "我们正在吃晚餐。"

# game/script.rpy:3155
translate chinese start_4529b742:

    # j "People don’t what?"
    j "一般人不会什么？"

# game/script.rpy:3162
translate chinese start_48046143:

    # g "Well... people don’t do {i}that{/i} at night... unless something happened to them."
    g "呃……一般人不会在夜里{i}那样{/i} ……除非他们遭遇过什么。"

# game/script.rpy:3164
translate chinese start_ff31a6a0:

    # j "I keep telling you, it must be some weird kind of insomnia."
    j "我和你说过很多次了，就是种很怪的失眠。"

# game/script.rpy:3165
translate chinese start_67521698:

    # j "Nothing more."
    j "没什么的。"

# game/script.rpy:3169
translate chinese start_16449281:

    # g "Sleeping pills don’t work on it."
    g "安眠药也不起作用。"

# game/script.rpy:3171
translate chinese start_f9307f01:

    # j "Something will, eventually."
    j "会有办法的。"

# game/script.rpy:3177
translate chinese start_af9e0171:

    # g "But why not try this?"
    g "那为什么不试试这个办法？"

# game/script.rpy:3183
translate chinese start_aa193693:

    # g "The memories you have... it's like they {i}want out.{/i}"
    g "你的记忆……好像它们想要找到{i}出口{/i}。"

# game/script.rpy:3187
translate chinese start_90c351c6:

    # g "I think they {i}should{/i} get out, too. Then you won’t be scared of whatever happened anymore."
    g "我也觉得它们{i}应该{/i}重见天日。那样你就不会再害怕发生的任何事了。"

# game/script.rpy:3189
translate chinese start_2ab4dafb:

    # j "And how does that work, exactly?"
    j "这样真的会有用么？"

# game/script.rpy:3193
translate chinese start_35c696da:

    # g "You’ll be able to face it properly."
    g "你会能好好面对的。"

# game/script.rpy:3197
translate chinese start_1ce2fca6:

    # g "It’s helped me a lot, you know. Thinking about... what happened to me. Seeing it’s not so bad as I thought it was."
    g "对我来说确实很有用，你看。想想……我身上发生的那些事。正视它们并没有我想象得那么糟。"

# game/script.rpy:3201
translate chinese start_3e031c32:

    # "I stubbornly refused to answer, and went on eating like there hadn’t been a conversation at all."
    "我固执地拒绝回答，继续吃饭，好像在此之前我们从未讲过话一样。"

# game/script.rpy:3207
translate chinese start_8c9efebd:

    # n "What Grace had referred to was something I’d only recently found out."
    n "格瑞丝所说的，我也是最近才知道的。"

# game/script.rpy:3208
translate chinese start_f1c518db:

    # n "Apparently I shouted and kicked at night a lot."
    n "显而易见，我经常在夜里大喊大叫，拳打脚踢。"

# game/script.rpy:3209
translate chinese start_b564785c:

    # n "Sometimes I all-out screamed."
    n "有时我会声嘶力竭地尖叫。"

# game/script.rpy:3211
translate chinese start_e3b814b6:

    # nvl clear
    # n "Maybe I still do all that, who knows?"
    nvl clear
    n "也许我现在依旧会这样，谁知道呢？"

# game/script.rpy:3214
translate chinese start_ca9e3216:

    # n "Maybe the staff and patients here are too polite to point it out."
    n "也许医院的医护人员和病友们不太好意思说出来。"

# game/script.rpy:3215
translate chinese start_5cdb9630:

    # n "No, I don't scream at night anymore."
    n "不，我不会在夜里尖叫了。"

# game/script.rpy:3216
translate chinese start_1fe62817:

    # n "I'm fairly sure I don't."
    n "我十分确定我不会了。"

# game/script.rpy:3217
translate chinese start_ee09f41c:

    # n "Though that's not to say I can sleep all that well."
    n "但这也并不是说我能在夜里安然入睡。"

# game/script.rpy:3219
translate chinese start_9372891e:

    # nvl clear
    # n "Funny how, at one point, something like that was the biggest problem in my life."
    nvl clear
    n "真有趣，这种事情曾一度是我人生中最严重的问题。"

# game/script.rpy:3222
translate chinese start_ef1f0b0c:

    # n "It was so long ago."
    n "已经是很久以前了。"

# game/script.rpy:3223
translate chinese start_1689dbfa:

    # n "Or at least it feels like so long ago."
    n "或者说至少感觉已经过了很久。"

# game/script.rpy:3224
translate chinese start_eba124e6:

    # n "So much has happened since then."
    n "从那之后发生了太多事情。"

# game/script.rpy:3226
translate chinese start_2ec3db94:

    # nvl clear
    # n "Anyway."
    nvl clear
    n "言归正传。"

# game/script.rpy:3229
translate chinese start_167adc81:

    # n "The morning after, I would wake up sweaty and tired, but it wasn’t until Grace told me about the screaming that I found out why."
    n "有时早晨醒来，我满头大汗，十分疲惫，但直到格瑞丝告诉我我会在夜里尖叫我才知道原因。"

# game/script.rpy:3231
translate chinese start_41b7d080:

    # nvl clear
    # n "Grace said it happened about once a week."
    nvl clear
    n "格瑞丝说这种情况大概一周会发生一次。"

# game/script.rpy:3234
translate chinese start_3424e3ee:

    # n "It really freaked her out, the first few times it happened. But then she got used to it."
    n "最初几次发生时，她吓坏了。但后来她渐渐习惯了。"

# game/script.rpy:3235
translate chinese start_2bde30db:

    # n "Or as used as you can get."
    n "或者说就像你一样接受了。"

# game/script.rpy:3237
translate chinese start_31d1f583:

    # nvl clear
    # n "It makes me feel like an asshole, realizing how nonchalant I was about it."
    nvl clear
    n "我觉得自己就是个混蛋，我意识到自己对此是多么冷漠。"

# game/script.rpy:3240
translate chinese start_31e991c3:

    # n "Screaming every few nights in my sleep was, I felt, a small price to pay so I wouldn’t have to bother with the past."
    n "我觉得几小晚的尖叫是微不足道的代价，这样我就不必再为过去而烦恼。"

# game/script.rpy:3242
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_39:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3246
translate chinese start_7888747a:

    # n "But it didn’t matter, in the end, if I decided to face the past or not."
    n "但结果，我决定是否面对过去并不重要了。"

# game/script.rpy:3247
translate chinese start_c07af154:

    # n "Either way it was coming."
    n "不管做出哪种选择，过去已经在步步逼近。"

# game/script.rpy:3249
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_40:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3257
translate chinese start_54b9e78f:

    # n "The second time Anna and I met as adults, we were neighbors."
    n "长大成人后我和安娜的第二次碰面，我们成为了邻居。"

# game/script.rpy:3259
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_41:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3267
translate chinese start_597ffa2e:

    # "I was coming back home from a morning shift at the store."
    "早班结束后，我回了家。"

# game/script.rpy:3277
translate chinese start_f5a40e85:

    # "I went into our building, up to the second floor, down the hall to mine and Grace's door—and I froze."
    "我走进我们的住宅楼，上到二楼，来到我和格瑞丝住处门前的大厅，我僵住了。"

# game/script.rpy:3278
translate chinese start_f5d19929:

    # "There was someone standing in front of our door."
    "有人站在我们的门前。"

# game/script.rpy:3300
translate chinese start_77e2175d:

    # "That someone was {i}her{/i}."
    "是{i}她{/i}。"

# game/script.rpy:3302
translate chinese start_c95efd22:

    # j "Anna."
    j "安娜。"

# game/script.rpy:3309
translate chinese start_e8d0305a_1:

    # a "Jack?"
    a "杰克？"

# game/script.rpy:3330
translate chinese start_317faf03:

    # a "Oh, goodness. What are you doing here?"
    a "噢，我的天，你在这儿干嘛？"

# game/script.rpy:3336
translate chinese start_104dc901:

    # a "Don’t tell me you...?"
    a "别告诉我你……？"

# game/script.rpy:3338
translate chinese start_9032855e:

    # "She pointed at the door, as if to ask if I lived there."
    "她指着那扇门，问我是不是住在这儿。"

# game/script.rpy:3340
translate chinese start_7417d75d:

    # j "Yes, that’s my apartment."
    j "对，我就住这儿。"

# game/script.rpy:3342
translate chinese start_53860b17:

    # "{i}As you damn well know.{/i}"
    "{i}你知道得可真清楚{/i}。"

# game/script.rpy:3343
translate chinese start_10066538:

    # "The hallway air felt warm and stale. Soup-like."
    "走廊里的空气温热腐旧，像浓汤一样浑浊。"

# game/script.rpy:3345
translate chinese start_16409cec:

    # j "What are {i}you{/i} doing here?"
    j "{i}你{/i}在这儿干什么？"

# game/script.rpy:3351
translate chinese start_b6d4249c:

    # a "I was going to say hello to my new neighbor."
    a "我正要去和我的新邻居问好呢。"

# game/script.rpy:3357
translate chinese start_a0aa9801:

    # a "So, hello."
    a "那么，你好。"

# game/script.rpy:3359
translate chinese start_43ac3e9b:

    # j "Wait, huh?"
    j "等等，哈？"

# game/script.rpy:3365
translate chinese start_a9c7403c:

    # a "And here."
    a "还有这个。"

# game/script.rpy:3372
translate chinese start_139ca699:

    # "She pushed something into my hands."
    "她往我手里塞了什么东西。"

# game/script.rpy:3373
translate chinese start_85ae07a4:

    # "It was a plate wrapped in plastic wrap. There was something brown on the plate."
    "是一个用保鲜膜裹住得盘子。盘子里有一些棕色的东西。"

# game/script.rpy:3377
translate chinese start_650824ba:

    # a "Brownies. I’m sure you’ll like them, Jack."
    a "是布朗尼。你肯定会喜欢的，杰克。"

# game/script.rpy:3379
translate chinese start_56ffd7d6:

    # j "But we’re {i}not{/i} neighbors!"
    j "但我们{i}不是{/i}邻居！"

# game/script.rpy:3383
translate chinese start_5f119f1e:

    # "I spat the words out."
    "我破口而出。"

# game/script.rpy:3390
translate chinese start_90f3a389:

    # a "Yes, we are."
    a "不，我们是。"

# game/script.rpy:3394
translate chinese start_24dff64b:

    # a "I’m right over there."
    a "我就住那边。"

# game/script.rpy:3398
translate chinese start_47366787:

    # "Anna showed me the door to the right of mine."
    "安娜指了指我们家右边的门。"

# game/script.rpy:3400
translate chinese start_ef5d6c7a:

    # j "Ah..."
    j "啊……"

# game/script.rpy:3402
translate chinese start_fead0e10:

    # "That place had been empty for weeks."
    "那间房已经空了好几个星期了。"

# game/script.rpy:3403
translate chinese start_e6248406:

    # "I'm pretty sure the guy who lived there before that was a heroin addict.{w} He didn’t seem so bad, now."
    "我很确定之前住在那里的那个人是个瘾君子。{w}现在看来，他似乎还是个不错的邻居。"

# game/script.rpy:3410
translate chinese start_63fea128:

    # a "What an amazing coincidence, though!"
    a "不过，多么巧啊！"

# game/script.rpy:3414
translate chinese start_b3d303c0:

    # a "To think we’d end up living so close by again."
    a "想想我们又再次住得这么近了。"

# game/script.rpy:3416
translate chinese start_77846eeb:

    # j "It’s not a coincidence, is it?"
    j "这不是巧合，对吗？"

# game/script.rpy:3420
translate chinese start_8929cfa8:

    # a "Pardon?"
    a "你说什么？"

# game/script.rpy:3422
translate chinese start_15dcb9b5:

    # j "Come on, really?"
    j "够了吧，好吗？"

# game/script.rpy:3423
translate chinese start_be275845:

    # j "What are you trying to do? It’s obvious you planned this."
    j "你到底想干什么？很明显你是故意的。"

# game/script.rpy:3424
translate chinese start_a6a0aecb:

    # j "There’s no way something like this could happen by accident."
    j "这样的凑巧绝不可能发生。"

# game/script.rpy:3430
translate chinese start_86e0fedc:

    # "Anna laughed. It was a sound like a fork scraping a plate."
    "安娜哈哈大笑。笑声听起来好像叉子划过盘子一样刺耳。"

# game/script.rpy:3432
translate chinese start_4f449b04:

    # j "Well?"
    j "嗯？"

# game/script.rpy:3438
translate chinese start_cc9fe5f1:

    # a "You can believe it’s a coincidence, or you can believe it’s not."
    a "就是巧合，信不信随你。"

# game/script.rpy:3442
translate chinese start_1fd39a3a:

    # a "Either way, we’ll be seeing each other pretty often."
    a "不管怎样，我们都能经常见面了。"

# game/script.rpy:3446
translate chinese start_89b4a066:

    # a "Enjoy the brownies."
    a "好好享用布朗尼吧。"

# game/script.rpy:3448
translate chinese start_5210cba0:

    # j "...Thanks."
    j "……谢了。"

# game/script.rpy:3449
translate chinese start_4c5b2514:

    # j "I’m not a big fan of sweet stuff, but I’m sure Grace will love them."
    j "我不太爱吃甜食，但我确定格瑞丝会喜欢它们。"

# game/script.rpy:3453
translate chinese start_d0092e92:

    # a "Grace?"
    a "格瑞丝？"

# game/script.rpy:3460
translate chinese start_b95ff0d4:

    # a "Who is Grace?"
    a "格瑞丝是谁？"

# game/script.rpy:3462
translate chinese start_c2baa11d:

    # j "My girlfriend."
    j "我女朋友。"

# game/script.rpy:3464
translate chinese start_f2fa124b:

    # "I pointed at our door with my thumb."
    "我用拇指指指我们家的门。"

# game/script.rpy:3466
translate chinese start_1db54964:

    # j "We live together."
    j "我们一起住。"

# game/script.rpy:3468
translate chinese start_a4ac2bca:

    # "My idea was that, in case she was acting like this because she was interested in me, I’d gently tell her I was taken."
    "我的想法是，如果她这样是因为她对我有兴趣，我就委婉地告诉她我已经有主了。"

# game/script.rpy:3476
translate chinese start_63029a80:

    # a "Grace."
    a "格瑞丝。"

# game/script.rpy:3478
translate chinese start_9f64a2bd:

    # j "Yes."
    j "是的。"

# game/script.rpy:3484
translate chinese start_4f099a79:

    # a "She must be a nice girl."
    a "她肯定是个很棒的女孩。"

# game/script.rpy:3486
translate chinese start_ac08cf3d:

    # j "The best I’ve ever known."
    j "是我遇见过的最好的女孩。"

# game/script.rpy:3492
translate chinese start_44bd3992:

    # a "She’s lucky to have you."
    a "有你这样的男朋友，她真幸运。"

# game/script.rpy:3494
translate chinese start_583ec612:

    # j "It’s the other way around."
    j "恰恰相反，我才是幸运的那一个。"

# game/script.rpy:3495
translate chinese start_0b23ca25:

    # j "Well, it’s been nice chatting."
    j "好了，和你聊得很愉快。"

# game/script.rpy:3496
translate chinese start_13a0d994:

    # j "I’ll say hi to Grace for you."
    j "我会替你向格瑞丝问好。"

# game/script.rpy:3502
translate chinese start_7498ad13:

    # a "I should go in and say hello myself."
    a "我要亲自去向她问好。"

# game/script.rpy:3506
translate chinese start_aca8e887:

    # j "No need."
    j "不用了。"

# game/script.rpy:3507
translate chinese start_2f55bc91:

    # j "And she’s not here right now."
    j "她现在不在家。"

# game/script.rpy:3513
translate chinese start_6985c9c7:

    # a "But—"
    a "可是——"

# game/script.rpy:3515
translate chinese start_b1c24079:

    # j "Bye."
    j "再见。"

# game/script.rpy:3521
translate chinese start_49c0f9bb:

    # "I pretended to unlock the door."
    "我假装打开门锁。"

# game/script.rpy:3522
translate chinese start_ed7ed507:

    # "It was already unlocked, because Grace was home."
    "其实门锁早就打开了，因为格瑞丝在家。"

# game/script.rpy:3528
translate chinese start_97e14f22:

    # "I slipped in and shut the door in Anna’s face."
    "我挤进屋，当着安娜的面把门关上了。"

# game/script.rpy:3532
translate chinese start_b75f6cb8:

    # "In the apartment, I found I could breathe freely again."
    "在我们的公寓里，我发现我又能通畅地呼吸了。"

# game/script.rpy:3534
translate chinese start_3c94fd22:

    # j "Son of a bitch..."
    j "贱人……"

# game/script.rpy:3536
translate chinese start_95d2f58b:

    # "Talk to this girl? Be friends with her?"
    "和这个女人说话？和她当朋友？"

# game/script.rpy:3537
translate chinese start_2b6269e9:

    # "Not a chance."
    "门都没有。"

# game/script.rpy:3538
translate chinese start_dba49481:

    # "She creeped the hell out of me."
    "她把我吓坏了。"

# game/script.rpy:3548
translate chinese start_469d171c:

    # n "Writing all this down, I can see why Grace thought I was overreacting."
    n "写下了这一切，我明白格瑞丝为什么觉得我反应过度了。"

# game/script.rpy:3549
translate chinese start_aba744bc:

    # n "The plain facts of it don’t seem that bad at all:"
    n "平淡简单的事实看起来没那么糟："

# game/script.rpy:3550
translate chinese start_a8f11143:

    # n "A friend I hadn’t seen in years noticed me at my workplace, talked with me a bit, and then happened to move in right next to me."
    n "一个我多年未见的朋友在我工作的商店里注意到了我，和我寒暄了几句，之后碰巧搬进了我家的旁边。"

# game/script.rpy:3551
translate chinese start_6ea96ec5:

    # n "But I knew right from the start that there was something {i}off{/i} about her. That’s not something to ignore."
    n "但我从一开始就知道她有些{i}不对劲{/i} ，这不容小觑。"

# game/script.rpy:3553
translate chinese start_a6e87747:

    # nvl clear
    # n "Paranoid? Yeah."
    nvl clear
    n "被害妄想？是的。"

# game/script.rpy:3556
translate chinese start_585a9565:

    # n "But in this case I was right to be paranoid."
    n "但是这次，我的妄想是对的。"

# game/script.rpy:3557
translate chinese start_07936a5f:

    # n "It’s because I let my guard down that all that shit happened."
    n "正是因为我放松了警惕，才发生了那种烂事。"

# game/script.rpy:3559
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_42:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3571
translate chinese start_da2b46bf:

    # n "Still no word from the doctor about when I’ll be able to get out of here."
    n "医生还是没有告诉我什么时候可以出院。"

# game/script.rpy:3572
translate chinese start_279da22b:

    # n "In fact I haven’t seen him in days. I hope he’s just busy."
    n "实际上我好几天都没见到他了。我希望他只是忙不过来。"

# game/script.rpy:3573
translate chinese start_a3b81825:

    # n "What if something happened to him?"
    n "万一他出事了呢？"

# game/script.rpy:3574
translate chinese start_3bc56451:

    # n "It’s the paranoia talking again."
    n "妄想症又开始了。"

# game/script.rpy:3576
translate chinese start_925e5d9f:

    # nvl clear
    # n "No, that’s not paranoia, that’s plain stupid. Anna can’t make a doctor disappear and get away with it."
    nvl clear
    n "不，这不是妄想症，这只是一般的白痴想法。安娜不可能在众人眼皮子底下让一个医生消失。"

# game/script.rpy:3579
translate chinese start_e6f3bcd3:

    # n "But I've got to say, if {i}this{/i} doctor did disappear, it wouldn’t be much of a loss to the hospital, I think."
    n "但我得说，我觉得，如果{i}这个{/i}医生真的不见了，这个医院也不会有太大损失。"

# game/script.rpy:3581
translate chinese start_87a9a35b:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I’ll have to ask him to give me some neck exercises I can do."
    nvl clear
    n "我得让他教我一些我能做的颈部运动。"

# game/script.rpy:3584
translate chinese start_f2d2a7ad:

    # n "My neck hurts from craning my head to the side all the time to look at the sky."
    n "我总是扭着头看天，这让我的颈椎很痛。"

# game/script.rpy:3585
translate chinese start_77b48d80:

    # n "Well, at least the weather’s bad now. I’m not looking there as much."
    n "好吧，至少现在天气很糟。我就不怎么看了。"

# game/script.rpy:3586
translate chinese start_95741a3d:

    # n "It’s weird how a little neck pain is causing me trouble, with how broken and battered the rest of me is."
    n "好奇怪啊，我身体的其他部分已经如此破碎不堪，怎么一点小小的颈部疼痛就会让我困扰。"

# game/script.rpy:3588
translate chinese start_5e05ba57:

    # nvl clear
    # n "No, I probably shouldn’t mention my neck to him."
    nvl clear
    n "不，也许我不该向他提起我的颈部。"

# game/script.rpy:3591
translate chinese start_73770c30:

    # n "They might up my dosage. And what’ll I do then, with my brain turned to mush?"
    n "他们可能会增加我的药量。我的大脑会变成一团浆糊，那我该怎么办？"

# game/script.rpy:3592
translate chinese start_fa138154:

    # n "Maybe then I’d be happy."
    n "也许我会开心起来。"

# game/script.rpy:3594
translate chinese start_6d6ad10b:

    # nvl clear
    # n "In any case, I have things to do, and I need a clear mind to do them."
    nvl clear
    n "不论如何，我还有事要做，我需要保持清醒的大脑。"

# game/script.rpy:3597
translate chinese start_a5b74a8c:

    # n "I hope that what I’m writing makes sense."
    n "我希望我写下的东西是通顺的。"

# game/script.rpy:3598
translate chinese start_fa350769:

    # n "I hope I haven’t gone down the rabbit hole already, and all I’m doing is scrawling line after line of meaningless chicken scratch."
    n "我希望我还没有越陷越深、无法脱身，我所做的就是一行接一行潦草写着无意义的句子。"

# game/script.rpy:3599
translate chinese start_eaeeee98:

    # n "But that’d be pretty funny, I guess. In a pretty unfunny way."
    n "但我想这很有趣。以一种无趣的方式来呈现的。"

# game/script.rpy:3601
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_43:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3609
translate chinese start_dd1657af:

    # n "August 12"
    n "8月12日"

# game/script.rpy:3610
translate chinese start_9e024ca7:

    # n "Anna’s brownies were tasty."
    n "安娜的布朗尼很美味。"

# game/script.rpy:3611
translate chinese start_4887a5a5:

    # n "I didn’t have any, but Grace said so."
    n "是格瑞丝说的，但我一口没吃。"

# game/script.rpy:3613
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_44:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3621
translate chinese start_641a82eb:

    # n "I wanted to throw the brownies into the trash, but Grace caught wind of them too quickly."
    n "我想把那些布朗尼扔了，但格瑞丝马上就注意到了。"

# game/script.rpy:3622
translate chinese start_f226c2b9:

    # n "She’s like a bloodhound when it comes to sweet stuff. Chocolate especially."
    n "她对甜食就像猎犬一样灵敏。对巧克力尤为如此。"

# game/script.rpy:3623
translate chinese start_b24ea532:

    # n "And then, of course, I had to explain where I’d got them."
    n "之后，理所当然的，我不得不解释它们是从哪来的。"

# game/script.rpy:3625
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_45:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3638
translate chinese start_b7f63f69:

    # g "Huh. Weird."
    g "哈。好怪。"

# game/script.rpy:3642
translate chinese start_89088885:

    # j "I know, right?"
    j "我知道，好吗？"

# game/script.rpy:3643
translate chinese start_b3eea09d:

    # j "There’s no way it’s a coincidence."
    j "不可能是巧合。"

# game/script.rpy:3649
translate chinese start_ea290a57:

    # g "Yeah. It must be a sign."
    g "对，这肯定是一种征兆。"

# game/script.rpy:3655
translate chinese start_d3b2a0e4:

    # "{i}A sign of what? That she’s stalking me?{/i}"
    "{i}什么征兆？她尾随我的征兆吗？{/i}"

# game/script.rpy:3661
translate chinese start_1854647e:

    # n "You know, it {i}is{/i} weird that she was stalking me—since she knew where I lived—but that she didn’t know about Grace."
    n "你懂的，她一直在跟踪我，{i}太{/i} 奇怪了。她知道我住哪儿，但是她不知道格瑞丝的存在。"

# game/script.rpy:3662
translate chinese start_adaa4fe4:

    # n "I mean, she couldn’t have known, with how surprised she was."
    n "我的意思是，看她吃惊的样子，她应该不知道。"

# game/script.rpy:3663
translate chinese start_1f64b4a3:

    # n "I don’t think she was acting."
    n "我不知道她是不是在演戏。"

# game/script.rpy:3665
translate chinese start_22b40d6d:

    # nvl clear
    # n "Was it just a coincidence, then?"
    nvl clear
    n "那这不会仅仅只是巧合吗？"

# game/script.rpy:3668
translate chinese start_08ee29f7:

    # n "No. Absolutely not."
    n "不是，绝对不可能的。"

# game/script.rpy:3669
translate chinese start_50196245:

    # n "{i}That{/i} I refuse to accept."
    n "{i}那样的话{/i} 我拒绝接受。"

# game/script.rpy:3671
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_46:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3682
translate chinese start_b10fd1eb:

    # g "I think I’ll go say hi."
    g "我觉得我应该去和她打个招呼。"

# game/script.rpy:3688
translate chinese start_4e5535ea:

    # g "I could make something for her, too."
    g "我也要做点什么吃的给她"

# game/script.rpy:3695
translate chinese start_619b8324:

    # g "Do we have any butter left? I want to bake her cookies."
    g "我们还有黄油吗？我想烤点曲奇饼给她。"

# game/script.rpy:3697
translate chinese start_52b45e31:

    # j "Yeah, and then you’ll eat most on your own."
    j "有，不过大部分都会被你吃掉。"

# game/script.rpy:3704
translate chinese start_60dfa3c4:

    # g "Hey!"
    g "嘿！"

# game/script.rpy:3706
translate chinese start_29dfce3c:

    # j "I don’t see the point of going to visit her, though."
    j "不过我觉得没必要特意去拜访她。"

# game/script.rpy:3707
translate chinese start_9504c676:

    # j "We’ll see more than enough of her anyway. We live so close by."
    j "我们以后还有得是时候碰面。我们就住隔壁。"

# game/script.rpy:3714
translate chinese start_e59ebb9a:

    # g "We’re neighbors. I want us to get started on the right foot."
    g "我们是邻居。我希望我们能有一个好的开始。"

# game/script.rpy:3718
translate chinese start_9c52db8e:

    # g "And maybe she and I could be friends."
    g "而且或许我和她能成为朋友。"

# game/script.rpy:3722
translate chinese start_87688cff:

    # g "I think that’d be nice."
    g "我觉得这很美好。"

# game/script.rpy:3729
translate chinese start_48bf1b04:

    # "I wrapped my arms around her."
    "我张开双臂抱住了她。"

# game/script.rpy:3731
translate chinese start_11fd0292:

    # j "Of course. You deserve that."
    j "当然，你值得体会这种美好。"

# game/script.rpy:3732
translate chinese start_2b3e809b:

    # j "But please, find a friend that’s not her."
    j "但是求你了，不要找她当朋友，另找别人吧。"

# game/script.rpy:3738
translate chinese start_cdd763bf:

    # g "Why?"
    g "为什么？"

# game/script.rpy:3742
translate chinese start_2f1fb294:

    # "Once again, I couldn’t properly explain why."
    "再一次，我无法好好解释原因。"

# game/script.rpy:3743
translate chinese start_8bcac75d:

    # "I couldn’t put it down as anything more than a hunch—a gut feeling I’d get whenever I was near her."
    "我只能说这是一种预感，只要我一接近她我就会有这种直觉。"

# game/script.rpy:3749
translate chinese start_e0053078:

    # g "I’ve at least got to see her for myself. To see if she’s really such a horrible person."
    g "至少我要亲眼见见她。看看她是不是真的这么可怕。"

# game/script.rpy:3751
translate chinese start_1b48ca19:

    # j "Trust me... you're better off without it."
    j "相信我……你最好不要去招惹她。"

# game/script.rpy:3765
translate chinese start_54289fe2:

    # n "The next day, in the afternoon, I was lying down on our sofa."
    n "第二天，下午，我躺在家里的沙发上。"

# game/script.rpy:3766
translate chinese start_4344c5fa:

    # n "I was nursing a headache that’d been with me since morning."
    n "我从早上就感到一阵头疼，我正在休养。"

# game/script.rpy:3768
translate chinese start_8bd36b05:

    # nvl clear
    # n "Grace told me she’d be right back."
    nvl clear
    n "格瑞丝和我说她马上就回来了。"

# game/script.rpy:3771
translate chinese start_74badc3d:

    # n "She went out of the apartment with something in her hands, and then a smell of freshly baked cookies wafted out of the kitchen."
    n "她手里拿着什么走出了公寓，一股刚出炉的曲奇饼芳香从厨房里飘来。"

# game/script.rpy:3772
translate chinese start_c68277fd:

    # n "It still took me about two minutes to piece the puzzle together."
    n "我花了大概两分钟才搞明白发生了什么。"

# game/script.rpy:3774
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_47:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3782
translate chinese start_2213401e:

    # n "\"Ah, shit,\" I whispered."
    n "“啊，该死。”我低语道。"

# game/script.rpy:3790
translate chinese start_44c23f04:

    # n "I was immediately up."
    n "我快速起身。"

# game/script.rpy:3792
translate chinese start_af75ec2c:

    # n "\"Not good, not good.\""
    n "“大事不妙，大事不妙。”"

# game/script.rpy:3794
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_48:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3800
translate chinese start_4a7e4181:

    # n "Panic struck me harder than I would expect."
    n "恐慌比我预想中来袭得更严重。"

# game/script.rpy:3801
translate chinese start_bb76b8de:

    # n "It was like, with Grace seeing Anna all by herself, some vulnerable part of me was exposed."
    n "格瑞丝独自去见安娜，就好像我最脆弱的部分暴露无遗。"

# game/script.rpy:3803
translate chinese start_13915a8e:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I wanted to bring Grace back and lock the door and keep her safe, and never, ever let her out of my sight."
    nvl clear
    n "我想带格瑞丝回来，把门好好锁住保证她平安无事，永远也不让她离开我的视线。"

# game/script.rpy:3811
translate chinese start_bf672cf3:

    # n "But I also didn’t want to go in there."
    n "但是我也不想进那间房子。"

# game/script.rpy:3813
translate chinese start_99a965c0:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I just stood there, head in my hands, wondering what the hell to do."
    nvl clear
    n "我就定定站在那儿，双手抱着头，不知道到底究竟该怎么办。"

# game/script.rpy:3821
translate chinese start_0623d455:

    # n "{w=0.5}All at once I was telling myself to go there, you coward, but also to stay here, you idiot, and somewhere far away a tiny little voice—very tiny, very little—was telling me I was overreacting..."
    n "{w=0.5}突然之间，我的内心一下对自己说，进去啊，你这个胆小鬼，一下又对自己说，别去，你这个蠢货。还有从远处传来一个细微的声音——非常非常飘渺——正对我说我反应过度了……"

# game/script.rpy:3823
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_49:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3830
translate chinese start_85d4d05b:

    # n "{w=0.75}Then there came the sound of glass breaking."
    n "{w=0.75}然后传来了玻璃碎掉的声音。"

# game/script.rpy:3831
translate chinese start_11206817:

    # n "It had come from—where else?—Anna’s apartment."
    n "这个声音来自——还有别处吗？——安娜的公寓。"

# game/script.rpy:3833
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_50:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3843
translate chinese start_25c2d629:

    # n "I went to the wall that separated our apartments."
    n "我走到隔着我们的公寓的墙边。"

# game/script.rpy:3844
translate chinese start_f0a8e575:

    # n "Now there was no sound at all. Nothing to explain the crash."
    n "现在一片沉寂。我对那破碎的声音摸不着头脑。"

# game/script.rpy:3846
translate chinese start_a7a414c1:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{w=1}I finally overcame my cowardice."
    nvl clear
    n "{w=1}最终我克服了我的胆怯。"

# game/script.rpy:3849
translate chinese start_eb39f527:

    # n "I dashed out from our apartment to hers."
    n "我跑出家门，冲向她的公寓。"

# game/script.rpy:3851
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_51:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3890
translate chinese start_8d54cd7a:

    # "When I got there I saw broken glass, and blood, and Grace kneeling down, and Anna stood above her, and—"
    "我冲进她家，看见了地上的碎玻璃和鲜血，格瑞丝正跪在地上，安娜直直地站在她身边。"

# game/script.rpy:3906
translate chinese start_69c8cee9:

    # "And they were both smiling."
    "她们两人都面带笑容。"

# game/script.rpy:3916
translate chinese start_7e9a4043:

    # "They stopped when they noticed me there, out of breath and confused."
    "她们注意到我气喘吁吁，一脸迷茫地杵在那儿，便停下手里的动作。"

# game/script.rpy:3918
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_52:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:3922
translate chinese start_cd7dbe1a:

    # g "Jack?"
    g "杰克？"

# game/script.rpy:3926
translate chinese start_645d41e8:

    # a "Hi, Jack. Did you decide to join us?"
    a "嗨，杰克。你终于下定决心加入我们啦？"

# game/script.rpy:3928
translate chinese start_54809d85:

    # j "No, I..."
    j "不，我……"

# game/script.rpy:3929
translate chinese start_efe6cd5c:

    # j "What the hell is going on?"
    j "究竟发生什么事了？"

# game/script.rpy:3942
translate chinese start_f83b7c9d:

    # a "This?"
    a "这个？"

# game/script.rpy:3946
translate chinese start_13da5eca:

    # "Anna waved her hand at the floor, at all the bits of glass—white ceramic, actually. There were also scattered cookies and drops of blood."
    "安娜朝着地面挥了挥手，地上满是细小的碎玻璃片——实际上是白色陶瓷。还有散落一地的曲奇饼和数滴鲜血。"

# game/script.rpy:3948
translate chinese start_6037f563:

    # j "Yes, that!"
    j "对，就是这个！"

# game/script.rpy:3950
translate chinese start_11142959:

    # "Just looking at the blood made me feel sick. Like I was going to throw up. But I couldn’t peel my eyes away from it."
    "光是看着这些血都让我感到恶心。我快要吐出来了。但我无法移开我的视线。"

# game/script.rpy:3951
translate chinese start_33d9943a:

    # "I’ve always been like that around blood. I’ve never had the stomach for it."
    "看见鲜血时我总会这样，感觉恶心想吐。"

# game/script.rpy:3952
translate chinese start_99e268bc:

    # "Grace was picking up the broken pieces of ceramic."
    "格瑞丝拿起一片陶瓷碎片。"

# game/script.rpy:3959
translate chinese start_f7adea30:

    # a "There was a little accident."
    a "出了点小意外。"

# game/script.rpy:3961
translate chinese start_59a6a45b:

    # j "An {i}accident{/i}?"
    j "{i}小意外{/i}？"

# game/script.rpy:3965
translate chinese start_c9eded5b:

    # a "Yes. What else?"
    a "对啊，不然呢？"

# game/script.rpy:3971
translate chinese start_96234fb4:

    # j "Grace, what happened?"
    j "格瑞丝，发生什么事了？"

# game/script.rpy:3980
translate chinese start_296421d0:

    # g "It’s my fault, really."
    g "是我的错，真的。"

# game/script.rpy:3984
translate chinese start_9b24f251:

    # g "The cookies were hotter than I thought, so I... dropped the whole plate."
    g "曲奇饼比我想象中还要烫，所以我……打碎了整个盘子。"

# game/script.rpy:3988
translate chinese start_c2d6fd80:

    # g "And it was Anna’s plate, too..."
    g "是安娜的盘子……"

# game/script.rpy:3992
translate chinese start_3d5993ba:

    # a "Be careful, Grace. You might cut yourself."
    a "小心一点，格瑞丝，别割伤了。"

# game/script.rpy:3994
translate chinese start_c6127747:

    # j "She’s cut herself already! Look!"
    j "她已经被割伤了！瞧！"

# game/script.rpy:4001
translate chinese start_0297fa45_1:

    # g "Huh?"
    g "啊？"

# game/script.rpy:4012
translate chinese start_7aa8f25c:

    # "She only now seemed to notice the blood around her."
    "她似乎现在才注意到周围流下的鲜血。"

# game/script.rpy:4018
translate chinese start_07097d8e:

    # g "B-But I..."
    g "但…但是我……"

# game/script.rpy:4022
translate chinese start_c6e8948e:

    # "Grace checked her hands—turned them around a few times to see from every angle—but found no cuts there."
    "格瑞丝检查了她的双手，翻来覆去看了好几遍，不放过任何角落，但都没有发现伤口。"

# game/script.rpy:4028
translate chinese start_bc0ee3c8:

    # g "...It’s not me."
    g "……我没受伤。"

# game/script.rpy:4036
translate chinese start_31747c67:

    # a "It’s my blood."
    a "是我的血。"

# game/script.rpy:4040
translate chinese start_a475dd4c_3:

    # j "What?"
    j "什么？"

# game/script.rpy:4056
translate chinese start_5e87590f:

    # "Anna was, I just noticed, holding her left hand tightly with her right."
    "我这才注意到，安娜正用右手紧紧握住了她的左手。"

# game/script.rpy:4057
translate chinese start_8cb761ce:

    # "There was a little blood still trickling from between her knuckles."
    "她的指间还渗出了一点鲜血。"

# game/script.rpy:4066
translate chinese start_7d56aab4:

    # g "Oh, no!"
    g "噢，不！"

# game/script.rpy:4070
translate chinese start_723e7140:

    # "Grace's hands hovered around Anna’s. She looked willing to help but afraid she’d do something wrong."
    "格瑞丝的手在安娜手周围悬停着。她看上去十分想帮忙但又害怕搞砸了。"

# game/script.rpy:4076
translate chinese start_7018a4c7:

    # g "H-How did this even happen?"
    g "这…这到底是怎么弄的？"

# game/script.rpy:4082
translate chinese start_6897e056:

    # a "I tried to pick up some of the pieces. They’re pretty sharp, aren’t they?"
    a "我试着捡起几块小碎片。它们真的很锋利，不是吗？"

# game/script.rpy:4088
translate chinese start_a82e6d03:

    # g "Hang on, Anna. I’ll..."
    g "坚持一下，安娜。我会……"

# game/script.rpy:4094
translate chinese start_91c78125:

    # a "I’m fine. I don’t need you to do anything."
    a "我没事。你不需要为我做什么。"

# game/script.rpy:4104
translate chinese start_2ca42917:

    # "The way Anna said that was forceful. Almost harsh."
    "安娜的语气很强硬。甚至有点刺耳。"

# game/script.rpy:4110
translate chinese start_6772b004:

    # "Grace backed away."
    "格瑞丝后退几步。"

# game/script.rpy:4117
translate chinese start_5b9c58b1:

    # g "I... I can still help!"
    g "我……我可以帮忙！"

# game/script.rpy:4124
translate chinese start_629ad6af:

    # "She remembered I was there."
    "她想起我在那。"

# game/script.rpy:4130
translate chinese start_17b723a1:

    # g "Jack, go get some gauze!"
    g "杰克，拿点纱布来！"

# game/script.rpy:4134
translate chinese start_0830284c:

    # j "...We have gauze?"
    j "……我们有纱布吗？"

# game/script.rpy:4141
translate chinese start_c17da9ee:

    # g "Oh, useless!"
    g "噢，没用！"

# game/script.rpy:4145
translate chinese start_33581529:

    # "Frustrated—more frustrated than I’d ever seen her before—Grace ran off to get the gauze herself."
    "格瑞丝一副沮丧的样子——我从未见过她如此沮丧——她自己跑去拿了纱布。"

# game/script.rpy:4146
translate chinese start_7e6bb726:

    # "She left me there, in the belly of the beast."
    "她将我留在原地，我如同身处兽腹之中。"

# game/script.rpy:4147
translate chinese start_55021bed:

    # "I tried being polite."
    "我试着维持礼貌。"

# game/script.rpy:4149
translate chinese start_df01f569:

    # j "Shame about the cookies."
    j "这些曲奇饼真可惜。"

# game/script.rpy:4155
translate chinese start_1ecb1721:

    # a "A real shame. I didn’t get to eat a single one."
    a "太遗憾了。我甚至一块都没尝过。"

# game/script.rpy:4159
translate chinese start_ae28e8b1:

    # a "Well, actually..."
    a "嗯，实际上……"

# game/script.rpy:4166
translate chinese start_761f359e:

    # "She picked one up with the free fingers of her left hand."
    "她用左手空闲的手指拿起一块。"

# game/script.rpy:4167
translate chinese start_36f945c2:

    # "Some of her blood got on the cookie."
    "曲奇饼上还有她的血。"

# game/script.rpy:4171
translate chinese start_51a3a0fb:

    # "Before I could say anything, she ate it in one bite."
    "在我出声之前，她便一口吃掉了。"

# game/script.rpy:4173
translate chinese start_e22c8981:

    # j "Jesus."
    j "天啊。"

# game/script.rpy:4179
translate chinese start_e941ece5:

    # a "It's not bad at all. They're still warm."
    a "味道还不错，它们还是热的。"

# game/script.rpy:4185
translate chinese start_5d5ef6de:

    # a "Do you want one?"
    a "你要尝尝吗？"

# game/script.rpy:4187
translate chinese start_357dc1f5:

    # j "I’ll pass."
    j "我不用了。"

# game/script.rpy:4188
translate chinese start_fabdf4bc:

    # j "God, you make me sick."
    j "天啊，你这么做让我感到不舒服。"

# game/script.rpy:4194
translate chinese start_9a9f8b37:

    # a "That’s not a very nice thing to say, Jack."
    a "这么说不好，杰克。"

# game/script.rpy:4198
translate chinese start_e427fe42:

    # a "If anyone else said it..."
    a "如果是其他人这么说……"

# game/script.rpy:4202
translate chinese start_70b23f3b:

    # a "But I’ll forgive you."
    a "但我原谅你。"

# game/script.rpy:4208
translate chinese start_d3ec7295:

    # "She licked her lips."
    "她舔了舔嘴唇。"

# game/script.rpy:4209
translate chinese start_cb7c47cf:

    # "I should have left. But I was like a frog being stared down by a snake."
    "我得走了。但我如同被蛇盯住的青蛙。"

# game/script.rpy:4211
translate chinese start_a3f40cd2:

    # j "I wonder what’s taking Grace so long."
    j "我好奇格瑞丝做什么花了这么久。"

# game/script.rpy:4217
translate chinese start_a25ee0c9:

    # a "She must be flustered. Poor girl."
    a "她一定很心慌。可怜的女孩。"

# game/script.rpy:4221
translate chinese start_39c79b6c:

    # a "So much worry about a teeny little cut."
    a "让你担心了，其实伤口很小。"

# game/script.rpy:4223
translate chinese start_ce1a21fb:

    # j "It’s not serious?"
    j "真的不要紧吗？"

# game/script.rpy:4227
translate chinese start_13fe7226:

    # a "It’s not."
    a "没事的。"

# game/script.rpy:4229
translate chinese start_b0d2f8cc:

    # j "How do you know?"
    j "你怎么确定？"

# game/script.rpy:4233
translate chinese start_243e4145:

    # a "I’ve seen a lot of cuts."
    a "我见过不少伤口。"

# game/script.rpy:4235
translate chinese start_04ce0fee:

    # j "I can imagine."
    j "我能估想出来。"

# game/script.rpy:4239
translate chinese start_0bceaff6:

    # "Anna laughed."
    "安娜笑着说。"

# game/script.rpy:4245
translate chinese start_e945081e:

    # a "I’m a nurse."
    a "我是个护士。"

# game/script.rpy:4249
translate chinese start_6cf4ec9a:

    # "That I couldn’t imagine."
    "我无法想象。"

# game/script.rpy:4250
translate chinese start_60b80d36:

    # "It’s still hard to believe, though I see proof of it every day."
    "即使我每天都能看到证据，但我还是很难相信。"

# game/script.rpy:4252
translate chinese start_e5799726:

    # j "There’s a lot of blood."
    j "你流了很多血。"

# game/script.rpy:4258
translate chinese start_030abdd0:

    # a "You don’t believe me?"
    a "你不相信？"

# game/script.rpy:4265
translate chinese start_735aee80:

    # a "Look."
    a "你看。"

# game/script.rpy:4267
translate chinese start_e6f4e514:

    # "She showed me her hand."
    "她给我看她的手。"

# game/script.rpy:4280
translate chinese start_d9ed5b0f:

    # "The cut ran from the base of her thumb towards the middle of her hand."
    "伤口从她的拇指根部一直延伸到手掌中部。"

# game/script.rpy:4281
translate chinese start_7eafb590:

    # "The wound was thin, but long and ragged."
    "伤口细长且不规整。"

# game/script.rpy:4282
translate chinese start_cc04752e:

    # "The skin around the wound was pale and moist, showing how fresh the cut was."
    "围绕伤口的皮肤苍白且湿润，表明伤口是新割的。"

# game/script.rpy:4283
translate chinese start_81a2e474:

    # "I could have puked."
    "我差点吐了。"

# game/script.rpy:4289
translate chinese start_1574f92e:

    # a "Oh, does it look bad?"
    a "噢，它看起来很糟？"

# game/script.rpy:4295
translate chinese start_9c4d0c3d:

    # a "Don’t worry, it won’t even scar."
    a "别担心，它甚至不会留疤。"

# game/script.rpy:4299
translate chinese start_264859b1:

    # j "Stop that!"
    j "停下！"

# game/script.rpy:4300
translate chinese start_57510cc3:

    # j "You’re really a—"
    j "你实在是个——"

# game/script.rpy:4302
translate chinese start_0cc52400:

    # "I don’t remember what I was going to say. It wasn’t nice, in any case."
    "我记不清我打算说什么，但无论怎么看都不是什么好话。"

# game/script.rpy:4308
translate chinese start_f9e63564:

    # "What stopped me was Grace coming back."
    "阻止我的是格瑞丝的归来。"

# game/script.rpy:4330
translate chinese start_193f486b:

    # g "Sorry, sorry!"
    g "不好意思，对不起！"

# game/script.rpy:4336
translate chinese start_bba9363b:

    # g "There wasn’t any gauze."
    g "家里没有纱布。"

# game/script.rpy:4340
translate chinese start_3920e508:

    # g "Here!"
    g "只有这个！"

# game/script.rpy:4342
translate chinese start_4784e1b1:

    # "She’d brought a roll of pink toilet paper."
    "她拿来了一卷粉色的厕纸。"

# game/script.rpy:4346
translate chinese start_f57398d6:

    # g "I hope this is good enough..."
    g "希望这能管用……"

# game/script.rpy:4350
translate chinese start_f187daec:

    # a "Thank you, Grace. But I don’t need it."
    a "格瑞丝，谢谢你。不过我不需要它。"

# game/script.rpy:4357
translate chinese start_6a4f4e56:

    # g "You don’t?"
    g "不用吗？"

# game/script.rpy:4361
translate chinese start_ffbda420:

    # a "No. See?"
    a "是的，你看？"

# game/script.rpy:4365
translate chinese start_3096c418:

    # a "The blood stopped."
    a "血止住了。"

# game/script.rpy:4385
translate chinese start_9b16d618:

    # "Anna flashed me a smile. The corners of her mouth were still red."
    "安娜丢给我一个微笑。她的嘴角仍是红色的。"

# game/script.rpy:4397
translate chinese start_924c7ed9:

    # n "August 13"
    n "8月13日"

# game/script.rpy:4398
translate chinese start_f03d571c:

    # n "Good day today. Didn’t see Anna once."
    n "今日是好日。一次都没见到安娜。"

# game/script.rpy:4399
translate chinese start_960f2820:

    # n "But enough of that."
    n "只是如此便足矣。"

# game/script.rpy:4401
translate chinese start_862cbf94:

    # nvl clear
    # n "After what happened—where I left off yesterday—I was sure Grace and I were on the same page."
    nvl clear
    n "那件事发生后——也就是我昨天停下来的地方——我确信格瑞丝与我同声同气。"

# game/script.rpy:4404
translate chinese start_b9e9d5b1:

    # n "But no."
    n "但其实并不是这样。"

# game/script.rpy:4406
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_53:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:4414
translate chinese start_1019219a:

    # "In the end, I was the one who cleaned up that bloody mess on the floor."
    "最终，我善后了地板上的血渍。"

# game/script.rpy:4415
translate chinese start_434a88a5:

    # "I threw away the cookies before Anna could get her hands on any more."
    "在安娜能再次拿到曲奇饼之前，我把它们都扔掉了。"

# game/script.rpy:4437
translate chinese start_17a18b26:

    # "Back in our apartment, Grace let out a long sigh."
    "回到我们的公寓后，格瑞丝长叹一声。"

# game/script.rpy:4439
translate chinese start_a059d0e9:

    # j "What a mess, am I right?"
    j "乱麻一团，是吧？"

# game/script.rpy:4445
translate chinese start_62dde6fd:

    # g "Yeah. And it was all my fault."
    g "是的。而这都是我的错。"

# game/script.rpy:4447
translate chinese start_67a9dcdc:

    # j "I meant Anna."
    j "我是说安娜。"

# game/script.rpy:4448
translate chinese start_bcf61793:

    # j "You did just meet her, right?"
    j "你刚结识她，对吧？"

# game/script.rpy:4452
translate chinese start_0a841025:

    # g "Yes?"
    g "是的，那怎么了吗？"

# game/script.rpy:4454
translate chinese start_257a711f:

    # j "And?"
    j "那么？"

# game/script.rpy:4461
translate chinese start_b51fe31a:

    # g "Well, I can see why you’ve been avoiding her."
    g "恩，也许我明白你为什么躲着她。"

# game/script.rpy:4465
translate chinese start_be7e96e2:

    # g "If that’s what you mean."
    g "如果你是这个意思的话。"

# game/script.rpy:4469
translate chinese start_5c413850:

    # j "{i}Thank{/i} you."
    j "{i}谢谢{/i}你。 "

# game/script.rpy:4473
translate chinese start_f792b4cd:

    # g "She’s..."
    g "她……"

# game/script.rpy:4479
translate chinese start_97ca28a7:

    # g "She’s beautiful."
    g "她很漂亮……"

# game/script.rpy:4485
translate chinese start_df994be4:

    # g "I thought she would be some shy little girl, or a crazy cat lady or something."
    g "我曾以为她会是个害羞的女孩，或者奇怪的独居女人之类的。"

# game/script.rpy:4491
translate chinese start_33ad7210:

    # g "But she’s like a model."
    g "但她就像个模特一样。"

# game/script.rpy:4493
translate chinese start_16d600a5:

    # j "What? No."
    j "什么？不是这样。"

# game/script.rpy:4499
translate chinese start_0c4a5e9e:

    # g "Don’t try to deny it, Jack."
    g "别尝试去否定这点，杰克。"

# game/script.rpy:4505
translate chinese start_c1d4d6fd:

    # g "It’s why you don’t want to go near her, isn’t it?"
    g "这就是你不想靠近她的原因，对吗？"

# game/script.rpy:4511
translate chinese start_7f0b1e01:

    # g "You don’t want to be tempted."
    g "你不想被她诱惑。"

# game/script.rpy:4513
translate chinese start_bbb7e3c6:

    # "I shook my head."
    "我摇了摇头。"

# game/script.rpy:4514
translate chinese start_55d234fd:

    # "I really didn’t see her that way."
    "我真不是这么看她的。"

# game/script.rpy:4515
translate chinese start_c6faf513:

    # "Now, with a little more perspective, I can say it’s true."
    "现在，从广阔一些的角度看，我可以承认这是真的。"

# game/script.rpy:4516
translate chinese start_c06dc046:

    # "What a waste of good looks."
    "徒具皮囊之美。"

# game/script.rpy:4523
translate chinese start_b2330749:

    # g "She’s much more beautiful than me..."
    g "她比我漂亮多了……"

# game/script.rpy:4525
translate chinese start_e4090092:

    # j "Hey, don’t say that. She’s not."
    j "嘿，别这么说，她没有。"

# game/script.rpy:4529
translate chinese start_fae9456f:

    # g "She is."
    g "她有。"

# game/script.rpy:4533
translate chinese start_0d71ddfe:

    # "Grace dropped her gaze to stare at her hands."
    "格瑞丝垂下目光，凝视着自己的手。"

# game/script.rpy:4540
translate chinese start_f81f3868:

    # g "And she wasn’t mad that I ruined her plate."
    g "而且，她没有因为我打碎了她的盘子而生气。"

# game/script.rpy:4544
translate chinese start_cec48d43:

    # g "She wasn’t scared of the blood, either."
    g "她也不怕血。"

# game/script.rpy:4550
translate chinese start_bca60d70:

    # g "She’s just so..."
    g "她是如此的……"

# game/script.rpy:4557
translate chinese start_19139aef:

    # "I took her hands in mine. They were cold."
    "我拢住她的手。她的手冰冷。"

# game/script.rpy:4559
translate chinese start_f0d57158:

    # j "Grace?"
    j "格瑞丝？"

# game/script.rpy:4566
translate chinese start_cd7dbe1a_1:

    # g "Jack?"
    g "杰克？"

# game/script.rpy:4568
translate chinese start_c2002d3e:

    # j "You’re beautiful. And kind. More beautiful and kind than any other girl in the world."
    j "你很美，而且善良，是世上最人美心善的女孩。"

# game/script.rpy:4569
translate chinese start_e9350ec4:

    # j "I'm lucky as hell to have you."
    j "能拥有你，我何其有幸。"

# game/script.rpy:4571
translate chinese start_a8e4be5d:

    # "My cheeks burned. I must’ve looked like a tomato."
    "我的脸颊烧起来了，我一定看起来像个番茄。"

# game/script.rpy:4572
translate chinese start_d341442a:

    # "I wasn’t used to saying stuff like this."
    "我不习惯说这种话。"

# game/script.rpy:4574
translate chinese start_aecab5fb:

    # j "I mean it."
    j "我是认真的。"

# game/script.rpy:4575
translate chinese start_73efa061:

    # j "So don’t say stuff like that."
    j "所以别说那样的话。"

# game/script.rpy:4576
translate chinese start_185f508f:

    # j "Okay?"
    j "好吗？"

# game/script.rpy:4584
translate chinese start_2a08bf92:

    # g "Oh..."
    g "噢……"

# game/script.rpy:4598
translate chinese start_fd90ed9a:

    # "Grace blinked like she’d just woken up."
    "格瑞丝眨着眼睛，就像她刚睡醒一般。"

# game/script.rpy:4604
translate chinese start_0bafd226:

    # g "O-Oh."
    g "嗯，噢。"

# game/script.rpy:4610
translate chinese start_29021d5b:

    # g "Um, I’ve been saying a lot of dumb stuff, I guess."
    g "呃，我猜我说太多蠢话了吧。"

# game/script.rpy:4614
translate chinese start_d921925a_1:

    # g "I'm sorry."
    g "对不起。"

# game/script.rpy:4620
translate chinese start_8d3314ce:

    # g "I'm a real hassle, huh?"
    g "我真是个麻烦吧？"

# game/script.rpy:4622
translate chinese start_07efcb9c:

    # j "No, don’t say that."
    j "不，别这么说。"

# game/script.rpy:4623
translate chinese start_c09d8701:

    # j "And don't say you're sorry, either."
    j "也不要说对不起。"

# game/script.rpy:4624
translate chinese start_6b93145d:

    # j "You’ve done nothing to feel sorry for."
    j "你没做任何需要道歉的事。"

# game/script.rpy:4626
translate chinese start_81ef1d82:

    # "She apologized way too often."
    "她总是在道歉。"

# game/script.rpy:4640
translate chinese start_0a6d6e08:

    # n "August 15"
    n "8月15日"

# game/script.rpy:4641
translate chinese start_2a98ff24:

    # n "I didn’t write anything yesterday. The pain in my leg made it so I couldn’t focus."
    n "我昨天什么都没写。腿上的疼痛使我无法集中注意力。"

# game/script.rpy:4642
translate chinese start_b5c14e3e:

    # n "It’s been hurting like a bitch these past few days."
    n "这些天一直疼得要死。"

# game/script.rpy:4643
translate chinese start_f4213fe7:

    # n "I gave in and asked the doctor about it."
    n "我屈服了，去问医生怎么办。"

# game/script.rpy:4645
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_54:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:4655
translate chinese start_f5afd4c5:

    # n "He’s fine, by the way. Didn’t disappear or anything. Must’ve taken a few days off."
    n "顺便说一句，他没事，既没失踪也没有别的什么。肯定只是请了几天假。"

# game/script.rpy:4657
translate chinese start_49a0200b:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I asked him about the pain. I asked if he could do anything about it."
    nvl clear
    n "我问他腿痛的事。我问他是否能为此做点什么。"

# game/script.rpy:4660
translate chinese start_94adede7:

    # n "Apparently the pain is a good sign. I think that’s what he said. So I guess my leg is healing all right."
    n "显然疼痛是个吉兆。我想他是这样说的。因此我猜测我的腿正在痊愈。"

# game/script.rpy:4662
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_55:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:4670
translate chinese start_21c9bf5a:

    # n "But it still hurts."
    n "但它还是作痛。"

# game/script.rpy:4671
translate chinese start_8cdaaaf8:

    # n "When the doctor went away, I complained out loud that it hurts."
    n "医生离开后，我大声抱怨起痛来。"

# game/script.rpy:4672
translate chinese start_ba604a17:

    # n "One of the other patients must have thought that I was talking to him."
    n "别的病人一定认为我是在和他说话。"

# game/script.rpy:4673
translate chinese start_12ef188e:

    # n "The patients here now are not the same guys I mentioned before. Maybe one is, but that’s all."
    n "现在这的病人不是我之前提过的那些。也许其中有一个是，但也仅此而已。"

# game/script.rpy:4675
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_56:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:4683
translate chinese start_7de1b0b7:

    # n "The others went away."
    n "其他病友都走了。"

# game/script.rpy:4684
translate chinese start_ab711be8:

    # n "To another part of the hospital, or home, or maybe to the morgue?"
    n "去了医院的其他部门，或者回家了，又或者在停尸房永眠?"

# game/script.rpy:4685
translate chinese start_4d60ca24:

    # n "I don’t know. I wasn’t keeping track."
    n "我不清楚。我没有持续关注。"

# game/script.rpy:4687
translate chinese start_e583baf6:

    # nvl clear
    # n "So I said something about how my leg hurt, and a guy on the bed next to mine—a kid, actually; can’t be more than eighteen or nineteen—starts talking to me."
    nvl clear
    n "所以我说说我的腿有多疼，以及我临床的一个家伙——实际上是个不超过十八九岁的孩子——开始同我说话的事吧。"

# game/script.rpy:4690
translate chinese start_d7db9e5d:

    # n "I think he was saying how he’s in a lot of pain, too."
    n "我想他是在说自己痛苦万分。"

# game/script.rpy:4692
translate chinese start_0f28714d:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I couldn’t understand most of it, though."
    nvl clear
    n "不过大部分我都不能理解。"

# game/script.rpy:4695
translate chinese start_524e2e0d:

    # n "His jaw’s been wired shut."
    n "他的下巴被金属线固定，合上了。"

# game/script.rpy:4696
translate chinese start_9d4f098d:

    # n "Anything he tries to say turns to moans and a lot of drool."
    n "他试着说的任何话都变成了呻吟和口水。"

# game/script.rpy:4697
translate chinese start_c754bf02:

    # n "Then a nurse came in—not Anna—and told him he shouldn’t speak if he wants his mouth to get better."
    n "然后一个护士进来了——不是安娜——告诉他，如果想让嘴好起来，他就不应该说话。"

# game/script.rpy:4698
translate chinese start_7d90a22c:

    # n "So he shut up."
    n "于是他沉默了。"

# game/script.rpy:4700
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_57:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:4708
translate chinese start_760cba94:

    # n "Not much else has happened."
    n "此外就没发生过什么了。"

# game/script.rpy:4709
translate chinese start_6130740f:

    # n "But my leg really is bothering me."
    n "但我的腿一直困扰着我。"

# game/script.rpy:4710
translate chinese start_2699aea8:

    # n "It’s a deep pain. It doesn’t feel like it’s healing."
    n "痛得厉害。感觉不像在愈合。"

# game/script.rpy:4711
translate chinese start_15684ad1:

    # n "It feels {i}wrong,{/i} in a way that makes my teeth hurt, too."
    n "感觉{i}不对劲，{/i}在某种程度上，这也让我牙痛。"

# game/script.rpy:4713
translate chinese start_b448052c:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I’ll stop with the leg now. I have to get my mind off it."
    nvl clear
    n "腿的事就说到这里吧，我需要换换思绪。"

# game/script.rpy:4716
translate chinese start_1f1002ea:

    # n "It hurts so much."
    n "好痛。"

# game/script.rpy:4717
translate chinese start_dca95bc3:

    # n "I’ll check where I left off the day before yesterday and go from there."
    n "我要检查一下前天停笔的地方并从那继续。"

# game/script.rpy:4719
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_58:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:4740
translate chinese start_0a86ec18:

    # g "You're not coming with us?"
    g "你不跟我们一起来吗？"

# game/script.rpy:4744
translate chinese start_e9ca5d8f:

    # g "Again?"
    g "再来一次吧？"

# game/script.rpy:4746
translate chinese start_3cacd284:

    # j "No, I don't feel like it."
    j "不，我不喜欢那样。"

# game/script.rpy:4751
translate chinese start_b38cfcad:

    # g "But Anna is so great to hang out with."
    g "但是安娜是个逛街的好伴。"

# game/script.rpy:4758
translate chinese start_0c9389be:

    # g "Yesterday we went window-shopping, then we went to a café, and then we had ice cream in the park..."
    g "昨天我们去逛了商店橱窗，然后去了咖啡馆，还在公园里一起吃了冰淇淋。"

# game/script.rpy:4760
translate chinese start_eb692f9e:

    # j "Sounds fun."
    j "听起来挺有意思的。"

# game/script.rpy:4767
translate chinese start_96b42ff5:

    # g "It was!"
    g "当然！"

# game/script.rpy:4771
translate chinese start_9218ada9:

    # g "Anna is a really interesting person. You should give her a chance."
    g "安娜很有趣。你应该给她一个机会。"

# game/script.rpy:4776
translate chinese start_6130b249:

    # g "I want us all to be friends."
    g "我希望我们都能做朋友。"

# game/script.rpy:4781
translate chinese start_7939140d:

    # g "So please come along?"
    g "所以，拜托了，一起来吧？"

# game/script.rpy:4783
translate chinese start_31dc83f7:

    # j "...No, I'll pass."
    j "……不，我不去了。"

# game/script.rpy:4787
translate chinese start_4a443ba0:

    # j "Sorry."
    j "对不起。"

# game/script.rpy:4789
translate chinese start_53d546e1:

    # "A moment later, Anna came in without knocking."
    "过了一会，安娜没敲门就进来了。"

# game/script.rpy:4801
translate chinese start_9be0c4e0:

    # "She never knocked anymore."
    "她再也没敲过门。"

# game/script.rpy:4805
translate chinese start_3dae7230:

    # a "Ready, Grace?"
    a "格瑞丝，准备好了吗？"

# game/script.rpy:4815
translate chinese start_794aa2dd:

    # g "Yes, in a minute."
    g "恩，马上就好。"

# game/script.rpy:4823
translate chinese start_e485f20e:

    # "Grace heaved a sigh."
    "格瑞丝叹了口气。"

# game/script.rpy:4830
translate chinese start_42bfaa70:

    # g "Are you sure you don't want to go?"
    g "确定不想跟我们去吗？"

# game/script.rpy:4832
translate chinese start_92abaae7:

    # j "Yes, I'm sure."
    j "我确定。"

# game/script.rpy:4833
translate chinese start_1ebc2333:

    # j "Go have fun without me."
    j "去玩吧，不用顾忌我。"

# game/script.rpy:4840
translate chinese start_9bde4cff:

    # g "...Okay, then. Some other time."
    g "……好吧。那，改日。"

# game/script.rpy:4852
translate chinese start_e7bc9f9b:

    # "We kissed."
    "我们相互亲吻。"

# game/script.rpy:4863
translate chinese start_09270180:

    # j "Have fun."
    j "玩得开心点。"

# game/script.rpy:4867
translate chinese start_9c402a50:

    # g "We will."
    g "我们会的。"

# game/script.rpy:4873
translate chinese start_418867d7:

    # g "Bye."
    g "再见。"

# game/script.rpy:4887
translate chinese start_548735d4:

    # n "Grace and Anna became friends."
    n "格瑞丝和安娜成为了朋友。"

# game/script.rpy:4900
translate chinese start_951c54e8:

    # n "Good friends. Very soon after they first met."
    n "在她们第一次见面后迅速成了很好的朋友。"

# game/script.rpy:4901
translate chinese start_992ed210:

    # n "I was against it, but I found it hard to complain, seeing Grace so happy."
    n "我抵触这点，但看到格瑞丝如此开心，我很难去抱怨。"

# game/script.rpy:4910
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_59:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:4914
translate chinese start_ba6d5191:

    # n "They spent quite a lot of time together."
    n "她们相伴了很多时光。"

# game/script.rpy:4915
translate chinese start_abb86544:

    # n "Whenever I said anything about this, Grace would tease me."
    n "每当我提起这件事，格瑞丝都会笑我。"

# game/script.rpy:4916
translate chinese start_92c23ad1:

    # n "She’d say I was jealous."
    n "她说我在嫉妒。"

# game/script.rpy:4917
translate chinese start_1b793436:

    # n "But she would also invite me to come with."
    n "但她也会邀请我一起去。"

# game/script.rpy:4918
translate chinese start_f72c10d1:

    # n "I always declined."
    n "我总是拒绝。"

# game/script.rpy:4920
translate chinese start_5243e057:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{w=0.5}I eventually got used to it."
    nvl clear
    n "{w=0.5}我最终习惯了。"

# game/script.rpy:4923
translate chinese start_7018dce2:

    # n "And things were quiet for a while."
    n "安稳度日了一段时间。"

# game/script.rpy:4927
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_60:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:4937
translate chinese start_fe28634f:

    # n "Once, at the store, I was applying discounts during work hours."
    n "有一次工作时间内，我在商店决定给什么打折。"

# game/script.rpy:4938
translate chinese start_bd90fc82:

    # n "It should’ve been done before we opened up, but someone had been slacking off."
    n "我们本该在开始营业前弄完的，但有人偷懒了。"

# game/script.rpy:4939
translate chinese start_162e3649:

    # n "I won’t point fingers."
    n "我不会推卸责任。"

# game/script.rpy:4940
translate chinese start_a60b74b4:

    # n "It was Don, the old guy."
    n "是唐在偷懒，那个老头。"

# game/script.rpy:4942
translate chinese start_012cd7bd:

    # nvl clear
    # n "So I was the one stuck wondering what kind of dog food the -20%% should go on, or something like that."
    nvl clear
    n "所以我一直在想什么狗粮应该打八折之类的事情。"

# game/script.rpy:4945
translate chinese start_e7091066:

    # n "The lists they gave us were always terrible, so full of corrections you could barely read them."
    n "他们给我们的清单总是乱七八糟，到处都是修改，让人几乎看不懂。"

# game/script.rpy:4949
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_61:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:4960
translate chinese start_93c79e32:

    # "As I was about to choose at random where to apply the discount sticker, someone put a hand on my shoulder."
    "我正要随机决定把折扣贴纸贴在哪时，有人把手放在了我的肩上。"

# game/script.rpy:4974
translate chinese start_6a77b8a7:

    # j "Oh. Anna."
    j "噢，安娜。"

# game/script.rpy:4986
translate chinese start_bf64b490:

    # "There was a tightness in my chest, but it passed within seconds."
    "我感到一阵胸闷，但几秒钟就好了。"

# game/script.rpy:4987
translate chinese start_d02e4988:

    # "As I said, I’d gotten used to it."
    "如我所说，我已经习惯了。"

# game/script.rpy:4988
translate chinese start_b443b715:

    # "She didn’t scare me anymore."
    "她没再吓我。"

# game/script.rpy:4994
translate chinese start_571277cd:

    # a "Hi."
    a "嗨。"

# game/script.rpy:5000
translate chinese start_f835390f:

    # a "How are you, Jack?"
    a " 最近怎么样，杰克？"

# game/script.rpy:5002
translate chinese start_9c1ef1b5:

    # j "I’m all right, thanks."
    j "挺好的，谢谢关心。"

# game/script.rpy:5003
translate chinese start_dcbbbf9b:

    # j "Hey, random question: Do you like big dogs or small dogs?"
    j "嘿，随便问问：你喜欢大狗还是小狗？"

# game/script.rpy:5009
translate chinese start_32fb53c2:

    # a "Hm?"
    a "嗯？"

# game/script.rpy:5017
translate chinese start_3890e0ac:

    # a "Big dogs, I guess."
    a "我觉得是大狗吧。"

# game/script.rpy:5021
translate chinese start_e7eb75b9_1:

    # j "I see."
    j "我明白了。"

# game/script.rpy:5023
translate chinese start_ec226dca:

    # "I bent down and placed the sticker, reducing the price of the dog food that had one of those wiener dogs on the packaging."
    "我弯下身子贴好贴纸，给包装上有腊肠犬的狗粮打了折。"

# game/script.rpy:5025
translate chinese start_6748d6bb:

    # j "Grace is in the break room, by the way."
    j "顺便一说，格瑞丝人在休息室。"

# game/script.rpy:5029
translate chinese start_297a5081:

    # a "I know, I was just there."
    a "我知道，我刚刚就是在那。"

# game/script.rpy:5036
translate chinese start_12140547:

    # a "But I wanted to see you."
    a "但我想见你。"

# game/script.rpy:5038
translate chinese start_34a6073b:

    # j "Yeah?"
    j "这样吗？"

# game/script.rpy:5039
translate chinese start_2fdefc32:

    # j "Why?"
    j "为什么？"

# game/script.rpy:5045
translate chinese start_9c4730b4:

    # a "I haven’t seen you at all for the past week, you know?"
    a "上个星期我一直都没见着你，你知道吗？"

# game/script.rpy:5049
translate chinese start_3685eb5f:

    # a "Didn’t you notice?"
    a "你没注意到吗？"

# game/script.rpy:5051
translate chinese start_e48e904c:

    # j "I guess."
    j "大概吧。"

# game/script.rpy:5057
translate chinese start_e8714847:

    # a "I was called into work a lot. And you must’ve been busy here, too."
    a "我总被叫去工作。你在这肯定也很忙吧。"

# game/script.rpy:5059
translate chinese start_e97ea1db:

    # j "Yep, busy-busy."
    j "是，忙——都忙。"

# game/script.rpy:5065
translate chinese start_38d79729:

    # a "We should meet more often."
    a "我们应该多见见面。"

# game/script.rpy:5069
translate chinese start_29511208:

    # a "After all these years apart, we must have a lot of stories to tell, huh?"
    a "多年分别之后，我们一定有不少故事可以讲吧？"

# game/script.rpy:5071
translate chinese start_7be43e66:

    # j "Yeah. Maybe."
    j "是啊，也许吧。"

# game/script.rpy:5077
translate chinese start_a20cefa7_3:

    # "..."
    "……"

# game/script.rpy:5081
translate chinese start_ecc527b1:

    # a "Jack, you mentioned dogs, right?"
    a "杰克，你提到了狗，对吧？"

# game/script.rpy:5085
translate chinese start_ad5179a6:

    # j "Right."
    j "是。"

# game/script.rpy:5091
translate chinese start_a86645db:

    # a "Was that because of Buddy?"
    a "是因为巴迪吗？"

# game/script.rpy:5093
translate chinese start_2356c73b:

    # j "Who’s Buddy?"
    j "巴迪是谁？"

# game/script.rpy:5100
translate chinese start_af3c2ab4:

    # a "Mmmmh."
    a "嗯。"

# game/script.rpy:5106
translate chinese start_3de03985:

    # a "So you really don’t remember anything?"
    a "所以你真的什么都不记得了？"

# game/script.rpy:5108
translate chinese start_3f2b586c:

    # j "Nope."
    j "是这样。"

# game/script.rpy:5109
translate chinese start_6663285f:

    # j "I don’t remember this Buddy, and I don’t remember knowing you, either."
    j "我不记得什么巴迪，也不记得我认识你。"

# game/script.rpy:5111
translate chinese start_e67e4593:

    # "Of course, now I do know about Buddy."
    "当然，我现在知道巴迪的事了。"

# game/script.rpy:5112
translate chinese start_573fb78b:

    # "I don’t remember his breed or how old he was—or anything other than his name, really—but I do know of him."
    "我不记得它的品种或者它多大了——除了它的名字我什么都不记得了——但我确信我知道它。"

# game/script.rpy:5113
translate chinese start_28f38c5e:

    # "A certain picture book told me."
    "A certain picture book told me."

# game/script.rpy:5120
translate chinese start_3957a793:

    # a "That's really too bad."
    a "真是太糟了。"

# game/script.rpy:5124
translate chinese start_42423bf5:

    # a "But it’ll all come back to you, I’m sure."
    a "我确信你会都想起来的。"

# game/script.rpy:5126
translate chinese start_32036233:

    # j "Who knows."
    j "谁知道呢。"

# game/script.rpy:5134
translate chinese start_bea3edc3:

    # a "Buddy was a really sweet dog. You liked him a lot."
    a "巴迪是一条很可爱的狗，你很喜欢它。"

# game/script.rpy:5138
translate chinese start_6bf8c3fd:

    # "I shrugged."
    "我耸了耸肩。 "

# game/script.rpy:5144
translate chinese start_2aa8fe0d:

    # a "And he {i}loved{/i} you. But then again, that dog loved everyone."
    a "它{i}爱{/i}你。不过话说回来，它每个人都喜欢。"

# game/script.rpy:5148
translate chinese start_295fc738:

    # a "He was so trusting."
    a "它太容易相信人了。"

# game/script.rpy:5150
translate chinese start_3cb41839:

    # "Too trusting?"
    "太轻信于人？"

# game/script.rpy:5152
translate chinese start_5203e122:

    # j "I’m sure he was."
    j "肯定是的。"

# game/script.rpy:5159
translate chinese start_f0fb6c92:

    # a "...Are you really fine with not knowing about so much of your life, Jack?"
    a "对自己的人生知之甚少，你真的能泰然处之吗，杰克？"

# game/script.rpy:5163
translate chinese start_ee21ae9b:

    # j "Yeah. I am. I’m used to it by now."
    j "是啊，我就是如此。如今我已经习惯了。"

# game/script.rpy:5164
translate chinese start_6bc024cd:

    # j "I think it would feel weird if I could remember, actually."
    j "我想，如果我能记起来会很奇怪。"

# game/script.rpy:5170
translate chinese start_6aac71e1:

    # a "I suppose it’s easier, in a way."
    a "我想在某种程度上，这样更轻松些。"

# game/script.rpy:5176
translate chinese start_f4f529ce:

    # a "There are some things best forgotten, after all. Aren’t there?"
    a "毕竟，有些事不如忘掉，是吧？"

# game/script.rpy:5178
translate chinese start_44a96754:

    # j "Hah, yeah."
    j "哈，是啊。"

# game/script.rpy:5184
translate chinese start_e8674e97:

    # n "Hah, yeah."
    n "哈，是啊。"

# game/script.rpy:5185
translate chinese start_54d7bd79:

    # n "Of course there are."
    n "当然有这样的事。"

# game/script.rpy:5186
translate chinese start_b6ae64cb:

    # n "And I wish some of those things would’ve had the decency to stay forgotten."
    n "而且我希望其中一些事能合情合理地被遗忘。"

# game/script.rpy:5188
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_62:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:5194
translate chinese start_fda4b2d8:

    # j "Why mention it now, though?"
    j "为什么你要现在提起来它呢？"

# game/script.rpy:5200
translate chinese start_41a752c4:

    # a "Oh, no reason."
    a "噢，没什么特别的理由。"

# game/script.rpy:5206
translate chinese start_78639f9f:

    # a "I was just a little curious."
    a "我只是有点好奇。"

# game/script.rpy:5208
translate chinese start_8d4d9a79:

    # j "Uh-huh."
    j "嗯哼。"

# game/script.rpy:5216
translate chinese start_b4cdaaa6:

    # n "I didn’t believe her."
    n "我不信任她。"

# game/script.rpy:5217
translate chinese start_a0b28bf9:

    # n "I sensed that there was something in particular she wanted me to remember."
    n "我感觉这其中有什么她想让我想起来的东西。"

# game/script.rpy:5218
translate chinese start_23756b40:

    # n "I do know what that is, now."
    n "现在我还不知道是什么。"

# game/script.rpy:5219
translate chinese start_056d0e67:

    # n "But I still don’t know {i}why{/i} she wants me to remember what she did."
    n "但我还是不知道{i}为什么{/i}她想要我记得她做过的事。"

# game/script.rpy:5221
translate chinese start_ae8aff28:

    # nvl clear
    # n "Is it some sick form of love? Or does she want to finish the job?"
    nvl clear
    n "是某种病态的爱吗？或是她要完成任务？"

# game/script.rpy:5224
translate chinese start_aa5ac382:

    # n "Is it both?"
    n "抑或两者都是？"

# game/script.rpy:5225
translate chinese start_562b43b2:

    # n "I don’t know. I really don’t."
    n "我不知道。我毫无头绪。"

# game/script.rpy:5226
translate chinese start_da61516e:

    # n "Her mind is as much of a mystery to me now as it ever was."
    n "对我而言，她的想法和过去一样是个谜。"

# game/script.rpy:5230
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_63:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:5248
translate chinese start_e79934f7:

    # y "Dear diary"
    y "亲爱的日记："

# game/script.rpy:5249
translate chinese start_d85e7f50:

    # y "I found him!"
    y "我遇见了他！"

# game/script.rpy:5250
translate chinese start_1272895a:

    # y "It was beautiful. It was like fate."
    y "如此美妙。宛若命运。"

# game/script.rpy:5251
translate chinese start_93ba0509:

    # y "It {i}was{/i} fate."
    y "{i}一定就是{/i}命运。"

# game/script.rpy:5253
translate chinese start_874f985b:

    # nvl clear
    # y "As soon as I came to this city, I caught his scent in the air!—a little, but mostly I smelled homeless people and gasoline."
    nvl clear
    y "我一来到这座城市，就在空气中捕捉到了他的气息！——虽然只有一点，而且我闻到的大部分是流浪汉和汽油的味道。"

# game/script.rpy:5256
translate chinese start_7d7c253b:

    # y "Why did you go all the way out here, Jack?"
    y "为什么你要跑到这么远的地方呢，杰克？"

# game/script.rpy:5257
translate chinese start_926ba3d6:

    # y "You love nature. The smell of pines. Where we grew up."
    y "你喜欢自然。喜欢松树的气味。那是我们一起长大的地方。"

# game/script.rpy:5259
translate chinese start_00a5d0bc:

    # nvl clear
    # y "I was ready to spend weeks looking for you, Jack."
    nvl clear
    y "我准备好花几周的时间来找到你，杰克。"

# game/script.rpy:5262
translate chinese start_9482e6f1:

    # y "Or months. Years, if I had to."
    y "也许要花几个月。甚至几年，如果我不得不如此的话。"

# game/script.rpy:5263
translate chinese start_a453bb47:

    # y "I even got a job at the hospital here. They’re understaffed, so it was easy."
    y "我甚至在医院找了个工作。他们人手不够，所以我很轻松地得到了工作。"

# game/script.rpy:5265
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_64:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:5273
translate chinese start_acdba15c:

    # y "But there you were. In the first store I went to."
    y "但你就在那儿。在我去的第一家商店里。"

# game/script.rpy:5274
translate chinese start_66f646aa:

    # y "I didn’t even go in to look for you."
    y "我甚至不是为了专门找你而j进去的。"

# game/script.rpy:5275
translate chinese start_a38ecccd:

    # y "Fate. Fate. Fate."
    y "命运。是命运。无可辩驳的命运。"

# game/script.rpy:5277
translate chinese start_cc4cd4ad:

    # nvl clear
    # y "But you were... a little strange."
    nvl clear
    y "但你……有一点奇怪。"

# game/script.rpy:5280
translate chinese start_6de9299f:

    # y "Surely you recognized me?"
    y "你真的认出我了吗？"

# game/script.rpy:5281
translate chinese start_1f4a0153:

    # y "I haven’t changed that much, have I?"
    y "我应该没有变太多吧，也许？"

# game/script.rpy:5282
translate chinese start_9d9af585:

    # y "I mean, it’s been a while, and I {i}have{/i} tried to make myself pretty for you (in every way I can think of), but you knew it was me, right?"
    y "我是说，有那么一段时间了，我{i}已经{/i}为了你而用我能想到的所有办法来使我自己变漂亮，但你知道那是我，对吧？"

# game/script.rpy:5283
translate chinese start_0858637a:

    # y "I knew it was you."
    y "我知道那是你。"

# game/script.rpy:5284
translate chinese start_5cb30c6e:

    # y "You haven’t forgotten me."
    y "你没有忘了我。"

# game/script.rpy:5286
translate chinese start_cce73fc6:

    # nvl clear
    # y "Were you pretending? Playing a game?"
    nvl clear
    y "你是在假装不认识我吗？同我玩一个游戏？"

# game/script.rpy:5289
translate chinese start_22e57db2:

    # y "Yes! That must be it."
    y "是！一定是这样。"

# game/script.rpy:5291
translate chinese start_b2cabb04:

    # nvl clear
    # y "Well, I’d love to wait and see what you’re doing, dear, but I've been a patient girl for far too long."
    nvl clear
    y "好吧，我乐于等等看你的下一步是什么，亲爱的，但耐心女孩如我，也已经等了太久了。"

# game/script.rpy:5295
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_65:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:5305
translate chinese start_e79934f7_1:

    # y "Dear diary"
    y "亲爱的日记："

# game/script.rpy:5306
translate chinese start_d45cff8e:

    # y "Friday."
    y "辛奇伍。"

# game/script.rpy:5307
translate chinese start_fe9bb6d5:

    # y "Jack Friday."
    y "杰克·辛奇伍。"

# game/script.rpy:5309
translate chinese start_2e0f6d14:

    # nvl clear
    # y "I knew he changed his name to that, but it’s just so funny, isn’t it!"
    nvl clear
    y "我得知他把名字换成了这个，但这很有意思，不是吗！"

# game/script.rpy:5312
translate chinese start_fbdfba14:

    # y "We’ll have to change it back, Jack. For when we’re married."
    y "我们必须把你的名字换回原来的，杰克。在我们结婚的时候。"

# game/script.rpy:5313
translate chinese start_4b2b12f8:

    # y "I want the {i}real{/i} one to follow my first name."
    y "我想要{i}真正的{/i}姓跟在我的名字后面。"

# game/script.rpy:5315
translate chinese start_5b571895:

    # nvl clear
    # y "Jack Friday."
    nvl clear
    y "杰克·辛奇伍。"

# game/script.rpy:5318
translate chinese start_66fb919c:

    # y "It made me giggle when I saw it in your employee records, darling."
    y "当我看到你雇员档案上的这名字时，我咯咯直笑，亲爱的。"

# game/script.rpy:5319
translate chinese start_f79127b5:

    # y "I just had a peek! Nothing more."
    y "我只是偷看了一下！别的什么都没干。"

# game/script.rpy:5320
translate chinese start_c0c3efd6:

    # y "Just to see where you live."
    y "只是看看你住在哪。"

# game/script.rpy:5321
translate chinese start_a6371f51:

    # y "I wanted to follow you home at first, but then I though—hey, wouldn’t it be {i}insanely{/i} romantic if the next time I saw you we lived right next to each other?"
    y "一开始，我想过跟着你回家，不过之后我想到——嘿，如果下次我见到你的时候我们就住在隔壁了，那是多么{i}狂乱的{/i}浪漫啊！"

# game/script.rpy:5323
translate chinese start_26595ae3:

    # nvl clear
    # y "I know you’re playing your little game of you-don’t-know-me-anymore, but that’s not too much, is it? Being neighbors?"
    nvl clear
    y "我知道你在玩你的小小游戏“你已经不认识我了”，但那已经过头了吧？我们做邻居如何？"

# game/script.rpy:5326
translate chinese start_5f1d4742:

    # y "You won’t be angry, right?"
    y "你不会生气的吧？"

# game/script.rpy:5327
translate chinese start_d3fd89d9:

    # y "Even if it makes you angry, I have to at least do this, right?!"
    y "即使你会因此生气，我也得至少这么做，一定是这样的吧？"

# game/script.rpy:5328
translate chinese start_1afd1a30:

    # y "I can’t wait anymore. I’m tired of being by myself."
    y "我无法再等。我厌倦了孑然一人。"

# game/script.rpy:5329
translate chinese start_c9732d84:

    # y "I’ve waited this long already. I’ve prepared for you so much."
    y "我已经等得够久了。为你我准备得够多了。"

# game/script.rpy:5331
translate chinese start_f68ea8ee:

    # nvl clear
    # y "Maybe you won’t be mad."
    nvl clear
    y "也许你不会生气。"

# game/script.rpy:5334
translate chinese start_8ed7e8ca:

    # y "Please don’t be mad."
    y "请不要生气。"

# game/script.rpy:5335
translate chinese start_43eb3793:

    # y "Please."
    y "求你了。"

# game/script.rpy:5337
translate chinese start_11267715:

    # nvl clear
    # y "P.S. One other thing, darling."
    nvl clear
    y "另外，还有一件事，亲爱的。"

# game/script.rpy:5340
translate chinese start_96a9ba9f:

    # y "That street where you live, isn’t it in a terrible part of town?"
    y "你住的那条街，是城里很糟糕的地方吧？"

# game/script.rpy:5341
translate chinese start_a64086cd:

    # y "Run-down and cheap and even dangerous?"
    y "破败廉价，甚至不安全。"

# game/script.rpy:5342
translate chinese start_62261149:

    # y "I haven’t been here for long, but I think that’s right."
    y "我来这不算久，但我想就是这样。"

# game/script.rpy:5343
translate chinese start_a20fdf1f:

    # y "Is that part of your game, too?"
    y "这也是你游戏的一部分吗？"

# game/script.rpy:5344
translate chinese start_64094c21:

    # y "And working in a store? That must be it as well."
    y "在商店里打工呢？肯定也是的。"

# game/script.rpy:5346
translate chinese start_6b309b00:

    # nvl clear
    # y "Someone like you should never work there."
    nvl clear
    y "像你这样的人应该永远不会在那工作。"

# game/script.rpy:5349
translate chinese start_8ae8f3a3:

    # y "Instead you should be a—"
    y "相反，你应该是个——"

# game/script.rpy:5350
translate chinese start_d6e99fe5:

    # y "Gosh, I can’t even imagine what."
    y "天啊，我甚至想不到。"

# game/script.rpy:5351
translate chinese start_385840e8:

    # y "And isn’t that perfect?"
    y "这样难道不是最好的吗？"

# game/script.rpy:5352
translate chinese start_9bde90bf:

    # y "I don’t want you working anywhere. I want you all for me."
    y "我不想你去任何地方工作，我想要你的一切。"

# game/script.rpy:5354
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_66:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:5364
translate chinese start_e79934f7_2:

    # y "Dear diary"
    y "亲爱的日记："

# game/script.rpy:5365
translate chinese start_713b7b65:

    # y "The street is worse than I thought."
    y "那条街道比我想的还糟。"

# game/script.rpy:5366
translate chinese start_5ca2d1b4:

    # y "God, the smell."
    y "天啊，那难以忍受的糟糕气味。"

# game/script.rpy:5367
translate chinese start_f8ad3154:

    # y "Do you really know what you’re doing, Jack?"
    y "你真的知道你在做什么吗，杰克？"

# game/script.rpy:5368
translate chinese start_f49d3993:

    # y "No, no, I shouldn’t doubt you. I know."
    y "不，不，我不应该怀疑你。我知道的。"

# game/script.rpy:5370
translate chinese start_60250e93:

    # nvl clear
    # y "The rent is cheap, at least. {i}Very{/i} cheap."
    nvl clear
    y "至少房租便宜。{i}非常{/i}廉价。"

# game/script.rpy:5373
translate chinese start_00ce6ab2:

    # y "But more important than that or anything else, there was a vacancy right next door to your apartment!"
    y "但是最重要的不是别的，而是在你隔壁有空屋！"

# game/script.rpy:5374
translate chinese start_0a2e4ac3:

    # y "I can’t wait to move in."
    y "我等不及要搬进去了。"

# game/script.rpy:5375
translate chinese start_032ec8e1:

    # y "We’ll be neighbors. I’ll see so much of you it will make me drunk."
    y "我们马上就要做邻居了。与你常见，如醉醇醪。"

# game/script.rpy:5377
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_67:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script.rpy:5389
translate chinese start_e79934f7_3:

    # y "Dear diary"
    y "亲爱的日记："

# game/script.rpy:5390
translate chinese start_56bbe7a0:

    # y "What a beautiful dump!"
    y "真是个漂亮的垃圾堆！"

# game/script.rpy:5391
translate chinese start_376f1efc:

    # y "I said this to the landlord when I brought my things here."
    y "我把行李搬过来的时候同房东这么说。"

# game/script.rpy:5392
translate chinese start_6da4e959:

    # y "He thought I was complaining. He said I should’ve checked out the apartment before I rented it."
    y "他以为我在抱怨。他说我搬进来前应该先仔细看看。"

# game/script.rpy:5393
translate chinese start_2c18cba3:

    # y "He’s an idiot."
    y "他什么都不懂。"

# game/script.rpy:5394
translate chinese start_57a97701:

    # y "There could be a swarm of rats or roaches living in the apartment, or crack addicts for that matter, and I wouldn’t give a darn."
    y "公寓里可能有成群的老鼠、蟑螂或者瘾君子，但我不在乎。"

# game/script.rpy:5396
translate chinese start_53bebcd3:

    # nvl clear
    # y "But still, I can’t keep it dirty forever."
    nvl clear
    y "但，我不能对脏乱一直无动于衷。"

# game/script.rpy:5399
translate chinese start_a32293ed:

    # y "I have to practice my homemaking skills."
    y "我不得不练习料理家务。"

# game/script.rpy:5400
translate chinese start_b79151d1:

    # y "Time to make this dump a home!"
    y "是时候变腐朽为家了！"

# game/script.rpy:5402
translate chinese start_76b2fe88_68:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

